-rule-for-mgnrega-workers%2Farticle67692863.ece%5C%22%3Edata%20by%20LibTech%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20a%20consortium%20of%20academics%20and%20activists%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnrega-job-card-deletions-aadhaar-mechanism-tech-solutions-ineffective%5C%22%3E7.6%20crore%20job%20cards%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20deleted%20from%20the%20system%20over%20the%20last%2021%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%20on%20Monday%2C%20Congress%20MP%20and%20the%20party%E2%80%99s%20media%20and%20communication%20in-charge%20Jairam%20Ramesh%20said%20that%20the%20move%20was%20the%20%E2%80%9Cprime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20cruel%20new%20year%20gift%20to%20exclude%20crores%20of%20the%20poorest%20and%20marginalised%20Indians%20from%20earning%20a%20basic%20income.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThere%20are%20in%20total%2025.69%20crore%20MGNREGA%20workers%20of%20whom%2014.33%20crore%20are%20considered%20as%20active%20workers.%20As%20on%20December%2027%2C%2034.8%25%20of%20the%20total%20registered%20workers%20(8.9%20crore)%20and%2012.7%25%20of%20active%20workers%20(1.8%20crore)%20are%20still%20ineligible%20for%20ABPS.%20Despite%20many%20challenges%20highlighted%20by%20workers%2C%20practitioners%2C%20and%20researchers%2C%20in%20using%20ABPS%20for%20MGNREGA%20wage%20payments%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20continued%20with%20its%20destructive%20%E2%80%98experiments%20with%20technology%E2%80%99.%20This%20is%20the%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20cruel%20new%20year%20gift%20to%20exclude%20crores%20of%20the%20poorest%20and%20marginalised%20Indians%20from%20earning%20a%20basic%20income%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERamesh%20accused%20the%20Modi%20government%20of%20using%20technology%20as%20a%20weapon%20to%20exclude%20the%20people%20belonging%20to%20the%20marginalised%20community.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20prime%20minister%E2%80%99s%20well-known%20disdain%20for%20MGNREGA%20has%20translated%20into%20a%20slew%20of%20experiments%20designed%20to%20use%20technology%20as%20a%20weapon%20to%20exclude%20%E2%80%93%20such%20as%20the%20digital%20attendance%20(NMMS)%2C%20ABPS%2C%20drone%20monitoring%2C%20and%20the%20proposed%20integration%20of%20facial%20recognition%20to%20NMMS.%20No%20due%20consultation%20or%20scientific%20piloting%20was%20done%20before%20unleashing%20these%20%E2%80%98experiments%E2%80%99%20on%20crores%20of%20Indians%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Congress%20reiterated%20its%20earlier%20demand%20that%20the%20Union%20government%20%E2%80%9Cshould%20stop%20weaponising%20technology%2C%20especially%20Aadhaar%2C%20to%20deny%20the%20most%20vulnerable%20Indians%20their%20social%20welfare%20benefits%2C%20release%20delayed%20wage%20payments%20and%20implement%20open%20muster%20rolls%20and%20social%20audits%20to%20improve%20transparency.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20popularity%2C%20the%20job%20scheme%20has%20seen%20budget%20cuts%20in%20recent%20years.%20In%20the%202023%20budget%2C%20the%20MGNREGS%20was%20allocated%20Rs%2060%2C000%20crore.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fnikhil-dey-mgnrega-budget-cut-2023%5C%22%3EConcerns%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20raised%20that%20the%20allocation%20to%20the%20MGNREGS%20has%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Fnrega-budget-allocation-2023-24%5C%22%3Edeclined%20by%2033%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20as%20compared%20to%20the%20revised%20estimates%20of%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%20%3C%2Fem%3Ehas%20earlier%20reported%20that%20the%20centrally%20sponsored%20scheme%20has%20not%20had%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fgovernment%2Fcag-audit-mgnrega-10-years-serious-questions%5C%22%3Eperformance%20audit%3C%2Fa%3E%20by%20the%20Comptroller%20and%20Auditor%20General%20(CAG)%20since%202013.%20CAG%E2%80%99s%20performance%20audits%20examine%20the%20extent%20to%20which%20an%20activity%2C%20programme%2C%20or%20organisation%20operates%20economically%2C%20efficiently%2C%20and%20effectively.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704107333000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2021%2F11%2F03131216%2FScreen-Shot-2021-11-03-at-1.07.58-PM.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcruel-new-year-gift-says-congress-as-mgnrega-wage-payment-through-aadhaar-system-kickstarts%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20implementation%20of%20an%20Aadhaar-based%20payment%20system%20was%20made%20mandatory%20on%20January%2030%2C%202023%2C%20and%20after%20five%20extensions%20for%20state%20governments%20to%20calibrate%20their%20databases%2C%20it%20is%20set%20to%20kickstart%20from%20January%201.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fcruel-new-year-gift-says-congress-as-mgnrega-wage-payment-through-aadhaar-system-kickstarts%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Here's%20what%20got%20cheaper%20and%20more%20expensive%20in%202023%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Customer%20showing%20prescription%20to%20pharmacist%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6335bf2125c9a90018a616d5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3E%3Cp%3EMorsa%20Images%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EInflation%20is%20down%2C%20but%20high%20prices%20on%20certain%20items%20are%20still%20hurting%20American%20wallets.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOne%20problem%20is%20day-to-day%20items%20are%20more%20likely%20to%20still%20have%20higher%20inflation.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EThings%20like%20used%20cars%20and%20airline%20tickets%20are%20cheaper%2C%20but%20aren't%20purchased%20as%20often.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Federal%20Reserve%20announced%20on%20December%2012%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finflation-consumer-price-index-november-economi