0series.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHer%20silk%20gown%20is%20perfect%2C%20as%20its%20exposed%20corset%2C%20jewel%20sleeves%2C%20and%20ruched%20skirt%20have%20an%20old-world%20feel%2C%20while%20her%20traditional%20veil%20makes%20her%20look%20like%20a%20bride.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20wears%20an%20embroidered%2C%20floral%20jacket%20until%20it's%20time%20for%20her%20outdoor%2C%20winter%20wedding%2C%20which%20feels%20even%20more%20fitting%20for%20her%20character.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAlthough%20Rachel%20Green's%20dress%20from%20the%20pilot%20is%20the%20most%20iconic%20%26quot%3BFriends%26quot%3B%20wedding%20dress%2C%20it%20feels%20more%20like%20a%20costume%20than%20a%20real%20gown.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221245%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22rachel%20wedding%20dress%20friends%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657a02f77a3c8094d5dca518%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22934%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERachel%20Green%20wears%20a%20wedding%20dress%20on%20the%20very%20first%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BFriends.%26quot%3B%20%3Cp%3ENBC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20Rachel%20is%20introduced%20on%20%26quot%3BFriends%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20appears%20at%20Central%20Perk%20in%20her%20wedding%20dress%2C%20looking%20for%20Monica%20after%20running%20out%20on%20her%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20gown%20is%20quintessential%20'90s%20wedding%20fashion%2C%20with%20its%20heavy%20lace%2C%20full%20skirt%2C%20and%20off-the-shoulder%20sleeves.%20But%20the%20whole%20look%20just%20feels%20gaudy%2C%20from%20the%20floral%20print%20on%20the%20skirt%20to%20the%20voluminous%20veil.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20considering%20the%20look%20went%20along%20with%20Rachel's%20spoiled%20persona%2C%20it%20was%20fitting%20for%20the%20occasion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EHilary%20Banks'%20wedding%20dress%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20Fresh%20Prince%20of%20Bel-Air%26quot%3B%20felt%20like%20a%20better%20take%20on%20a%201990s%20wedding%20gown.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg