houlder%20dress%20is%20easily%20one%20of%20our%20favorites%20on%20this%20list.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNashville%26quot%3B%20costume%20designer%20Susie%20DeSanto%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.glamour.com%2Fstory%2Fnashville-rayna-wedding-dress%23%3A~%3Atext%3DDeSanto%2520told%2520People.-%2C%2522Like%2520her%2520character%252C%2520the%2520dress%2520is%2520simple%252C%2520honest%252C%2Chand%252Dsewn%2520lace%2520flower%2520appliques.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EGlamour%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202016%20that%20she%20wanted%20the%20dress%20to%20reflect%20Rayna's%20character%20and%20be%20%26quot%3Bsimple%2C%20honest%2C%20not%20too%20fussy%2C%20elegant%2C%20and%20sophisticated.%26quot%3B%20DeSanto%20said%20she%20showed%20sketches%20to%20Connie%20Britton%2C%20who%20played%20Rayna%20in%20the%20show%2C%20and%20ultimately%20wanted%20to%20create%20the%20kind%20of%20wedding%20dress%20%26quot%3Byou%20wear%20when%20you%20marry%20your%20true%20love.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dress%20featured%20a%20lace%20bodice%20and%20satin%20skirt%20designed%20with%20lace%20flower%20appliqu%C3%A9%20that%20was%20sewn%20on%20by%20hand%2C%20according%20to%20Glamour.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAlthough%20she%20didn't%20end%20up%20getting%20married%2C%20April%20Kepner's%20dress%20was%20one%20of%20the%20best%20%26quot%3BGrey's%20Anatomy%26quot%3B%20wedding%20gowns%20of%20all%20time.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221464%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22April%20Kepner%20stands%20at%20her%20wedding%20altar%20on%20%26quot%3BGreys%20Anatomy%26quot%3B%20surrounded%20by%20her%20bridal%20party.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657a2a190ec98e92f74f3800%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221098%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EApril%20Kepner%20is%20one%20of%20the%20many%20characters%20we%20see%20tie%20the%20knot%20on%20%26quot%3BGrey's%20Anatomy.%26quot%3B%20%3Cp%3EABC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EApril's%20season%2010%20wedding%20became%20famous%20for%20%26quot%3BGrey's%20Anatomy%26quot%3B%20fans%2C%20as%20she%20ends%20up%20running%20away%20with%20Jackson%20and%20marrying%20him%20instead%20of%20her%20fianc%C3%A9%2C%20Matthew.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20her%20dress%20was%20almost%20as%20memorable%20as%20the%20episode%20itself.%20The%20short-sleeve%20dress%20had%20sheer%2C%20short%20sleeves%20that%20flowed%20into%20an%20adorned%20bodice%2C%20creating%20the%20illusion%20that%20appliqu%C3%A9%20was%20floating%20up%20her%20torso.%20The%20dropped-waist%20skirt%20was%20adorned%20with%20flowers%2C%20and%20the%20gown%20flowed%20into%20a%20train.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20hard%20to%20see%20why%20Jackson%20interrupted%20the%20wedding%20to%20whisk%20April%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ELikewise%2C%20Cristina%20Yang%20didn't%20marry%20Preston%20Burke%2C%20but%20the%20dress%20she%20wore%20to%20their%20wedding%20was%20stunning.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Christina%20Yang%20stands%20in%20a%20wedding%20dress%20on%20%26quot%3BGreys%20Anatomy.%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657a064a7a3c8094d5dca84c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222343%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ECristina%20was%20meant%20to%20wear%20this%20dress%20during%20her%20first%20wedding%20on%20%26quot%3BGrey's%20Anatomy.%26quot%3B%20%3Cp%3EABC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EPreston%20left%20Cristina%20at%20the%20altar%20in%20the%20season%20three%20finale%20of%20%26quot%3BGrey's%20Anatomy%2C%26quot%3B%20though%20the%20bride-to-be%20had%20been%20apprehensive%20about%20the%20idea%20of%20getting%20married%2C%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20not%20wanting%20to%20be%20a%20bride%2C%20she%20looked%20every%20bit%20the%20part%20in%20her%20mermaid%20gown.%20Christina's%20lace%20dress%20was%20adorned%20with%20understated%20silver%20embellishments%2C%20and%20her%20updo%20showed%20off%20the%20choker%20Preston's%20mother%20gave%20her%20to%20wear%20at%20the%20wedding.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20dress%20was%20gorgeous%3B%20it%20was%20just%20odd%20to%20see%20Cristina%20Yang%20wearing%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ESummer%20and%20Seth%20finally%20got%20their%20happy%20ending%20on%20%26quot%3BThe%20O.C.%26quot%3B%20series%20finale%2C%20but%20the%20wedding%20dress%20wasn't%20special%20enough.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221399%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Summer%20Roberts%20wedding%20on%20The%20O.C.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657cb8877a3c8094d5ddb369%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221050%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESummer%20walks%20down%20the%20aisle%20during%20the%20series%20finale%20of%20%26quot%3BThe%20O.C.%26quot%3B%20%3Cp%3EFOX%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20the%20preppy%20shirts%20and%20Juicy%20Couture%20tracksuits%20to%20the%20halter%20tops%20and%20lace%20camis%2C%20Summer's%20closet%20perfectly%20encapsulated%20the%20pure%20boldness%20of%20early%202000s%20fashion.%20She%20loved%20bright%20colors%2C%20bold%20patterns%2C%20and%20graphic%20T-shirts%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0matching%20her%20spunky%20and%20outspoken%20personality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMaybe%20the%20costume%20department%20was%20trying%20to%20illustrate%20Summer's%20character%20arc%20from%20trendy%20teen%20to%20vegan%20queen%20by%20picking%20this%20simple%20wedding%20dress.%20We%20love%20a%20classic%20moment%2C%20but%20the%20bodice%20is%20ill-fitting%20and%20completely%20swallows%20Rachel%20Bilson's%20figure%2C%20while%20the%20full%20skirt%20just%20looks%20wrinkled.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPlus%2C%20it's%20just%20a%20little%20boring.%20After%20four%20seasons%20of%20watching%20Summer%20and%20Seth's%20love%20story%2C%20we%20would've%20loved%20Summer's%20dress%20to%20feel%20a%20little%20more%20memorable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EJessa's%20shotgun%20wedding%20dress%20was%20also%20a%20miss%20in%20what%20could've%20been%20a%20fun%20bohemian%20style%20moment%20for%20%26quot%3BGirls.%26quot%3B%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%22980%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Jessa's%20wedding%20day%20on%20%26quot%3BGirls%26quot%3B%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657cb7bc50edbc52a864f129%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221224%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EJessa%20surprised%20everyone%20with%20her%20wedding%20during%20the%20season%20one%20finale%20on%20%26quot%3BGirls.%26quot%3B%20%3Cp%3EHBO%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20%26quot%3BGossip%20Girl%26quot%3B%20was%20a%20fantasy%20of%20NYC%20fashion%2C%20%26quot%3BGirls%26quot%3B%20set%20out%20to%20be%20the%20reality%20with%20off-the-rack%20clothes%20meant%20to%20reflect%20what%20women%20really%20wear%20in%20the%20city.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESo%20at%20first%20glance%2C%20the%20short%20and%20casual%20dress%20seems%20to%20fit%20Jessa's%20eccentric%20style.%20But%20%26quot%3BGirls%26quot%3B%20costume%20designer%20Jenn%20Rogien%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffashionista.com%2F2012%2F06%2Fgirls-costume-designer-on-that-wedding-jessas-crazy-feather-outfit-and-what-to-expect-from-season-two%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EFashionista%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202014%20that%20Lena%20Dunham%20wanted%20the%20cast%20to%20%26quot%3Blook%20the%20best%20they%20had%20all%20season%26quot%3B%20at%20the%20wedding.%20Rogien%20said%20she%20looked%20at%20both%20vintage%20and%20runway%20pieces%20and%20ultimately%20decided%20on%20this%20dress%20at%20a%20boutique%20owned%20by%20the%20mother%20of%20Jemima%20Kirke%2C%20who%20plays%20Jessa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20story%20behind%20the%20outfit%20is%20great%2C%20but%20the%20dress%20doesn't%20fit%20the%20major%20twist%20of%20the%20season%20finale.%20We%20love%20the%20cutout%20detailing%20on%20the%20oversized%20sleeves%2C%20but%20they%20clash%20with%20the%20lacy%20skirt.%20The%20overall%20look%20just%20feels%20too%20casual%2C%20more%20akin%20to%20something%20you%20would've%20found%20at%20Free%20People%20in%202012.%20There%20are%20so%20many%20beautiful%20vintage%20and%20boho%20bridal%20looks%2C%20but%20this%20just%20feels%20forgettable%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0and%20that's%20definitely%20the%20opposite%20of%20Jessa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWilhelmina%20Slater%20might%20have%20been%20the%20villain%20in%20%26quot%3BUgly%20Betty%2C%26quot%3B%20but%20she%20looked%20like%20a%20dream%20in%20this%20Vera%20Wang%20gown%20during%20her%20wedding.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221763%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Wilhemina%20Slater's%20wedding%20day%20on%20Ugly%20Betty%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657cb9e77a3c8094d5ddb43c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221322%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWilhelmina%20Slater's%20wedding%20was%20an%20iconic%20episode%20of%20%26quot%3BUgly%20Betty.%26quot%3B%20%3Cp%3EABC%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EFrom%20an%20organ%20remix%20of%20%26quot%3BMilkshake%26quot%3B%20to%20a%20guest%20appearance%20by%20Victoria%20Beckham%20playing%20herself%2C%20there%20was%20a%20lot%20happening%20during%20Wilhelmina%20Slater's%20wedding%20in%20the%20second%20season%20of%20%26quot%3BUgly%20Betty.%26quot%3B%20But%20that%20didn't%20stop%20the%20former%20supermodel%20and%20MODE%20magazine%20editor%20from%20stealing%20the%20show.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWilhelmina%20walked%20down%20the%20aisle%20in%20a%20luxurious%20silk%20gown%20designed%20by%20Vera%20Wang%2C%20who%20also%20played%20herself%20during%20the%20episode.%20The%20strapless%20column%20dress%20only%20features%20a%20touch%20of%20sparkling%20embellishment%2C%20letting%20the%20cut%20of%20the%20gown%20and%20its%20stunning%20fabric%20take%20center%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20also%20loved%20how%20Wilhelmina%20paired%20the%20dress%20with%20matching%20silk%20elbow-length%20opera%20gloves.%20The%20ensemble%20couldn't%20have%20been%20a%20better%20match%20for%20our%20favorite%20stylish%20supervillain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ERobin%20Scherbatsky's%20wedding%20dress%20in%20%26quot%3BHow%20I%20Met%20Your%20Mother%26quot%3B%20could've%20been%20a%20showstopper.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221370%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Robin's%20wedding%20day%20on%20How%20I%20Met%20Your%20Mother%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F657cba2f0ec98e92f750274b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221028%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERobin%20and%20Barney's%20wedding%20day%20is%20on%20the%20ninth%20and%20final%20season%20of%20%26quot%3BHow%20I%20Met%20Your%20Mother.%26quot%3B%20%3Cp%3ECBS%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20several%20major%20story%20decisions%20that%20confused%20fans%20during%20the%20ninth%20and%20final%20season%20of%20%26quot%3BHow%20I%20Met%20Your%20Mother.%26quot%3B%20But%20we're%20here%20to%20talk%20about%20Robin%20and%20Barney's%20wedding%2C%20not%20that%20wild%20twist%20in%20the%20series%20finale.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERobin%20opts%20for%20a%20Monique%20Lhuillier%20gown%20to%20wed%20the%20reformed%20womanizer%2C%20and%20there's%20a%20lot%20we%20love%20about%20it.%20The%20exposed%20corset%20is%20a%20modern%20and%20unexpected%20style%20choice%2C%20and%20it%20pairs%20well%20with%20the%20sheer%20sleeves%20that%20hang%20just%20off%20her%20shoulders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20all%20gets%20ruined%20with%20the%20big%2C%20sparkling%2C%20silver%20belt.%20Not%20only%20does%20the%20design%20of%20the%20belt%20seem%20dated%2C%20especially%20when%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20gown%20feels%20so%20fresh%2C%20but%20it%20cuts%20off%20Robin's%20body%20and%20throws%20off%20the%20proportions%20of%20the%20ensemble%2C%20messing%20up%20what%20could%20have%20been%20a%20very%20chic%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20combination%20of%20beading%20and%20a%20bow%20on%20the%20bodice%20of%20Lily%20Aldrin's%20dress%20didn't%20work.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221338%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22lily%20how%20i%20met%20your%20mother%20wedding%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5b1593eb5e48ec3e008b45f2%3