20I%20skipped%20eating%20beef%20but%20ate%20some%20chicken.%20My%20diet%20was%20mostly%20seafood%2C%20vegetables%2C%20and%20noodles.%20I%20was%20pleased%20that%20the%20UAE%20made%20sustainable%20foods%20readily%20available%20during%20COP28%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cop28.com%2Fen%2Fnews%2F2023%2F11%2FCOP28-to-offer-15C-aligned-menus-across-more-than-90-culinary-outlets%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etwo-thirds%20of%20menu%20options%3C%2Fa%3E%20were%20plant-based.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20a%20lot%20of%20variety%2C%20from%20Arabic%20street%20food%20to%20Japanese%20sweets%20and%20Vietnamese%20noodles.%20Prices%20were%20comparable%20to%20the%20US%2C%20ranging%20from%20%2412%20to%20%2435%20for%20lunch.%20I%20appreciated%20plant-based%20innovators%20like%20Switch%20Foods%2C%20a%20UAE-based%20startup%2C%20but%20their%20kebab%20sandwiches%20weren't%20very%20filling.%20I%20preferred%20restaurants%20that%20weren't%20totally%20plant-based%20but%20had%20a%20lot%20of%20meatless%20options.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDuring%20my%20personal%20time%2C%20I%20had%20no%20issues%20eating%20vegetarian%20either%3A%20Dubai%20has%20many%20Mediterranean%2C%20Indian%2C%20Chinese%2C%20and%20Thai%20restaurants%20where%20vegetarian%20dishes%20are%20plentiful.%20Dinner%20can%20be%20on%20the%20expensive%20side.%20My%20Indian%20takeout%20came%20to%20%2431%20and%20many%20well-known%20restaurants%20are%20in%20upscale%20hotels%20and%20can%20cost%20at%20least%20%24100%20per%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20my%20five%20favorite%20dishes%20from%20my%20visit%20to%20Dubai%2C%20and%20why%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3ECeviche%20from%20Mama%20Zonia%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223022%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Ceviche%20in%20a%20bowl%20on%20ice%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658dd3b7ab6f2ebb11f7803d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223879%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EClassic%20ceviche.%3Cp%3ECatherine%20Boudreau%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EMama%20Zonia%20is%20a%20Latin-inspired%20restaurant%20with%20an%20Asian%20twist%2C%20located%20in%20Dubai%20Marina.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fqr.emenu.ae%2Fdxpkg6onma%2F%23%2Fcategory%2F1130%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emenu%20has%20a%20mix%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20Latin%20American%20favorites%20like%20ceviche%20and%20grilled%20Picanha%2C%20a%20cut%20of%20beef%20popular%20in%20Brazil%2C%20plus%20Japanese%20staples%20like%20sushi%20and%20udon%20noodles.%20There%20is%20also%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fqr.emenu.ae%2Fdxpkg6onma%2F%23%2Fcategory%2F20954%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ea%20special%20vegan%20menu%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20classic%20ceviche%20is%20made%20with%20raw%20sea%20bass%20in%20a%20citrus%20marinade%2C%20roasted%20sweet%20potato%2C%20coriander%2C%20and%20roasted%20corn%20kernels%20%E2%80%94%20known%20as%20cancha%20in%20countries%20like%20Peru.%20It%20was%20fresh%2C%20flavorful%2C%20and%20nearly%20as%20delicious%20as%20the%20ceviche%20I%20tried%20in%20Peru.%20It%20cost%20nearly%20%2419.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20also%20loved%20the%20mixed%20mushroom%20cazuela%2C%20a%20dish%20popular%20in%20Chile%20named%20for%20the%20clay%20pot%20it's%20served%20in.%20Mama%20Zonia%20gave%20it%20an%20Asian%20flair%2C%20with%20Korean%20BBQ%20sauce%2C%20congee%20rice%2C%20and%20lots%20of%20ginger%2C%20garlic%2C%20and%20sesame%20oil.%20The%20price%20was%20nearly%20%2426.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECome%20for%20the%20food%2C%20stay%20for%20the%20views.%20Mama%20Zonia%20has%20a%20terrace%20overlooking%20Dubai%20Marina%20and%20colorful%2C%20jungle-themed%20decor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EFalafel%20salad%20from%20Habib%20Beirut%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Falafel%20salad%20with%20cucumbers%20and%20pickled%20vegetables%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658ddeb01c5c7b8c9a0ca9bb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223261%5C%