Chillers.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ordered%20all%20four%20chiller%20flavors%20from%20a%20kiosk%3A%20Mexican%20Chocolate%2C%20Dulce%20de%20Leche%20Coffee%2C%20Wild%20Strawberry%2C%C2%A0and%20Sweet%20Vanilla.%C2%A0All%20four%20drinks%20cost%20%244.19%20for%20a%2016-ounce%20cup.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Mexican%20Chocolate%20chiller%20looked%20chocolatey%2C%20but...%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taco%20Bell%20Mexican%20Chocolate%20Chiller%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6583552acefc010bea25d80e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Taco%20Bell%20Mexican%20Chocolate%20Chiller%20looked%20chocolatey.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%E2%80%A6%20it%20wasn't%20heavy%20on%20the%20chocolate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresentation-wise%2C%20the%20drink%20looked%20inviting%20with%20chocolate%20swirls%2C%20a%20thick%20cold%20foam%20topping%2C%20and%20churro%20crumbles.%20I%20commend%20the%20staff%20for%20making%20the%20drink%20look%20like%20the%20marketing%20images%2C%20something%20that%20doesn't%20always%20happen%20with%20fast%20food%20pictures.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETexture-wise%2C%20the%20drink%20was%20a%20bit%20icy%2C%20like%20a%20Wendy's%20Frosty.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20a%20chocolate%20fan%2C%20you%20might%20be%20disappointed%20in%20this%20one.%20%26quot%3BIt%20tastes%20like%20brown-colored%20ice%2C%26quot%3B%20my%20dining%20partner%2C%20who%20is%20an%20admitted%20chocoholic%2C%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Dulce%20de%20Leche%20Coffee%20drink%20tasted%20nothing%20like%20coffee.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221800%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Dulce%20de%20Leche%20Coffee%20at%20Taco%20Bell%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65835beca79e5746976be8d0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221350%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Dulce%20de%20Leche%20Coffee%20drink%20is%20part%20of%20the%20Churro%20Chiller%20lineup%20because%20it%20contains%20churro%20crumbles%20and%20less%20caffeine%20than%20the%20Coffee%20Chillers%2C%20Taco%20Bell%20said.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Dulce%20de%20Leche%20Coffee%20drink%20is%20misnamed.%20It%20doesn't%20taste%20anything%20like%20coffee.%20It%20was%20cloyingly%20sweet%20compared%20to%20the%20chocolate%20shake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20dulce%20de%20leche%2C%20which%20means%20%26quot%3Bsweet%20milk%26quot%3B%20in%20Spanish%2C%20should%20taste%20like%20candy.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cold%20foam%20and%20churro%20crumbles%2C%20which%20are%20topped%20on%20all%20of%20the%20chiller%20drinks%2C%20made%20this%20beverage%20even%20sweeter%20if%20that's%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ELater%2C%20I%20asked%20Taco%20Bell%20about%20the%20shake's%20coffee%20content.%20They%20told%20me%20it%20is%20blended%20with%20coffee%2C%20but%20the%20caffeine%20content%20is%20less%20than%2050%20milligrams.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20probably%20why%20I%20didn't%20taste%20any%20coffee.%20The%20sugary%20base%20devoured%20the%20small%20amount%20of%20coffee%20in%20the%20shake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E(Note%3A%20The%20average%20amount%20of%20caffeine%20in%20an%208-ounce%20cup%20of%20brewed%20coffee%20is%2096%20milligrams%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ffdc.nal.usda.gov%2Ffdc-app.html%23%2Ffood-details%2F1104137%2Fnutrients%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUSDA%3C%2Fa%3E.)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETaco%20Bell's%20Sweet%20Vanilla%20Chiller%20is%20the%20most%20innovative%20of%20the%20four%20shakes.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taco%20Bell's%20Sweet%20Vanilla%20Chiller%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658362aba79e5746976bf295%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaco%20Bell's%20Sweet%20Vanilla%20Chiller%20is%20a%20very%20pretty%2C%20on%20brand%20drink.%20%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20something%20comforting%20about%20a%20plain%20vanilla%20shake.%20But%20Taco%20Bell%20doesn't%20do%20plain%2C%20so%20they%20added%20a%20%26quot%3Bpurple%26quot%3B%20swirl%20in%20the%20shake.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20wanted%20to%20try%20this%20shake%20with%20a%20spoon%20to%20get%20a%20perfect%20blend%20of%20blended%20vanilla%2C%20churro%20crumbles%2C%20and%20cold%20foam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20alas%2C%20Taco%20Bell%20doesn't%20have%20spoons!%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20ended%20up%20using%20a%20fork%20to%20scoop%20up%20the%20thick%20shake%20with%20a%20few%20crumbles%20and%20cold%20foam%2C%20which%20is%20impossible%20to%20do%20with%20a%20straw.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThere%20was%20nothing%20wild%20or%20innovative%20about%20the%20Wild%20Strawberry%20chiller.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taco%20Bell%20Strawberry%20Chiller%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658360351c5c7b8c9a0aae6e%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaco%20Bell's%20Strawberry%20Chiller%20had%20an%20artificial%20taste.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ETaco%20Bell's%20Wild%20Strawberry%20chiller%20was%20my%20least%20favorite%20of%20the%20four%20drinks.%20The%20artificial%20flavoring%20of%20the%20strawberry%20was%20overpowering.%20It%20tasted%20like%20Nesquik%20Strawberry%20milk.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cold%20foam%20and%20churro%20crumbles%20could%20not%20save%20this%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOverall%2C%20I%20liked%20the%20Churro%20Chillers%20a%20lot.%20I%20especially%20like%20the%20price.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224032%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taco%20Bell%20is%20calling%20its%20new%20cold%20drinks%20Coffee%20Chillers%20and%20Churro%20Chillers.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65835035a79e5746976bdbdb%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223024%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaco%20Bell%20staff%20in%20Irvine%2C%20California%20did%20a%20good%20job%20in%20making%20my%20chillers%20look%20like%20the%20marketing%20photos.%20%3Cp%3EFoodbeast%20for%20Taco%20Bell%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EShakes%20are%20a%20tough%20segment%20to%20muscle%20into.%20Chains%20like%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-it-costs-to-open-a-chick-fil-a-2016-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EChick-fil-A%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Dairy%20Queen%2C%20and%20Sonic%20are%20known%20for%20their%20delicious%20shakes.%20But%20Taco%20Bell%20is%20off%20to%20a%20good%20start.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%244.19%20price%20tag%20is%20competitive.%20Most%20Chick-fil-A%20shakes%20cost%20at%20least%20%245%20or%20more%2C%20according%20to%20prices%20listed%20on%20the%20chain's%20app%20in%20Orange%20County%2C%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3ETaco%20Bell%20is%20testing%20three%20different%20Coffee%20Chillers%2C%20which%20contain%20caffeine%20that's%20nearly%20equal%20to%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222016%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taco%20Bell%20Coffee%20Chillers%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6583ad3a1c5c7b8c9a0abcf2%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221512%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETaco%20Bell%20is%20testing%20three%20Coffee%20Chillers%20at%20one%20store%20in%20Southern%20California.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20next%20day%2C%20I%20drove%20to%20Mission%20Viejo%2C%20California%20to%20try%20the%2016-ounce%20iced%20coffee%20chillers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETaco%20Bell%20is%20testing%20three%20flavors%3A%20Mexican%20Chocolate%2C%20Caramel%20Churro%2C%20and%20Spiced%20Vanilla.%20The%20caffeine-infused%20drinks%20are%20topped%20with%20cold%20foam.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Coffee%20Chillers%20contain%20about%2075%20to%2080%20milligrams%20of%20caffeine%2C%20nearly%20equal%20to%20a%20cup%20of%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Mexican%20Chocolate%20Coffee%20Chiller%20tasted%20just%20like%20the%20chocolate%20churro%20shake%20but%20with%20a%20hint%20of%20coffee.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221494%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Mexican%20Chocolate%20Coffee%20Chiller%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6583ada3cefc010bea25f45f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221080%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EI%20wish%20the%20churro%20crumbles%20came%20with%20the%20Coffee%20Chillers.%20%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20drink%20was%20nearly%20identical%20to%20its%20Churro%20Chiller%20counterpart.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20taste%20only%20a%20hint%20of%20coffee.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThese%20drinks%20do%20not%20contain%20churro%20crumbles%2C%20which%20is%20a%20bummer%20because%20the%20crumbles%20are%20fun%20and%20provide%20a%20much-needed%20crunchy%20texture.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIf%20you're%20looking%20for%20a%20strong%2C%20mocha-style%20frappe%2C%20I%20think%20you'll%20be%20disappointed%20in%20this%20beverage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Spiced%20Vanilla%20Coffee%20Chiller%20was%20the%20least%20exciting%20drink%20to%20look%20at.%20But%20it%20was%20sweet%20and%20satisfying.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221780%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20Spiced%20Vanilla%20Coffee%20Chiller%20at%20Taco%20Bell%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6583aea5a79e5746976bfe45%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221165%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Spiced%20Vanilla%20Coffee%20Chiller%20at%20Taco%20Bell%20didn't%20look%20very%20good%2C%20but%20it%20sure%20was%20sweet.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20vanilla%20drink%20looked%20boring%20compared%20to%20the%20Sweet%20Vanilla%20shake%20with%20the%20purple%20swirls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20it%20was%20delicious.%20I%20don't%20drink%20frappe%20drinks%20because%20they're%20too%20sweet.%20But%20I%20would%20order%20this%20one%20on%20a%20hot%20summer%20afternoon.%20The%20sweet%20vanilla%20flavor%20mixed%20with%20a%20subtle%20amount%20of%20coffee%20made%20this%20a%20very%20approachable%20drink.%20It%20was%20not%20too%20indulgent.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYou%20also%20can't%20beat%20the%20price%20at%20%244.19.%20A%2016-ounce%20Caffe%20Vanilla%20Frappuccino%20cost%20%245.95%20at%20my%20local%20Starbucks%20in%20Orange%2C%20California.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EThe%20Caramel%20Churro%20coffee%20chiller%20was%20my%20favorite%20of%20the%20three%20frozen%20iced%20coffee%20drinks.%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221543%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taco%20Bell%20Coffee%20Chiller%20Caramel%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6583ae291c5c7b8c9a0abcfa%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221053%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20Caramel%20Churro%20coffee%20chiller%20was%20good%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20taste%20any%20churro%20flavors.%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EBy%20the%20time%20I%20had%20this%20drink%2C%20I%20realized%20that%20I%20needed%20to%20stir%20it%20with%20my%20straw%20to%20get%20a%20better%20taste%20of%20all%20the%20ingredients.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECaramel%20streaks%20were%20visible%20on%20this%20drink%2C%20but%20much%20of%20the%20thick%20and%20sticky%20topping%20had%20pooled%20to%20the%20bottom%20of%20the%20drink.%20So%20stirring%20was%20necessary%20to%20get%20a%20perfect%20sip%20of%20the%20sugary%20goodness%20in%20this%20drink.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20my%20favorite%20drink%20of%20the%20three%20Coffee%20Chillers%20because%20the%20caramel%20and%20coffee%20flavors%20paired%20well.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EOverall%2C%20I%20liked%20the%20shakes%20the%20best%20because%20of%20the%20cold%20foam%20and%20churro%20crumbles.%20%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221889%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Taco.%20Bell%20is%20testing%20churro%20chillers%20in%20California.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6583b134a79e5746976bfe5a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221277%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EThe%20churro%20crumbles%20gave%20the%20Churro%20Chillers%20an%20edge%20over%20the%20Coffee%20Chillers.%20%3Cp%3ENancy%20Luna%2FBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20seven%20drinks%20were%20topped%20with%20Taco%20Bell's%20version%20of%20cold%20foam%20%E2%80%93%20a%20thick%2C%20sweet%20buttermilk%20base%20foam%20topping%20that%20tasted%20like%20whipped%20cream.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%2C%20the%20churro%20crumbles%20gave%20the%20shakes%20an%20edge%20over%20the%20Coffee%20Chillers.%20The%20crumbles%20added%20texture%2C%20which%20was%20missing%20in%20the%20blended%20frozen%20coffee%20drinks.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20love%20to%20see%20the%20Sweet%20Vanilla%20and%20Dulce%20de%20Leche%20Coffee%20shakes%20and%20the%20Caramel%20Churro%20and%20Spiced%20Vanilla%20coffee%20chillers%20expand%20nationally.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20a%20little%20more%20work%20in%20the%20test%20kitchen%2C%20I%20think%20the%20Mexican%20Chocolate%20shake%20and%20coffee%20chiller%20could%20make%20the%20national%20menu.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20would%20note%20that%2C%20operationally%2C%20Taco%20Bell%20needs%20to%20figure%20out%20how%20to%20serve%20these%20drinks%20faster.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20waited%20a%20long%20time%20for%20both%20drinks%20to%20be%20served.%20I%20can%20see%20this%20being%20an%20issue%20in%20the%20drive-thru.%20But%20that's%20why%20tests%20are%20necessary.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20sure%20Taco%20Bell%20will%20work%20out%20the%20kinks.%20And%2C%20when%20they%20do%2C%20Taco%20Bell%20fans%20will%20likely%20turn%20up%20in%20droves.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EAre%20you%20a%20fast-food%20insider%20with%20insight%20to%20share%3F%20Got%20a%20tip%3F%20Contact%20this%20reporter%20via%