3EShe%20says%20the%20first%20step%20in%20reaching%20your%20goals%20is%20not%20relying%20on%20your%20future%20self%20to%20handle%20it.%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3EOnce%20you%20take%20accountability%2C%20ensure%20the%20goals%20align%20with%20your%20values%20and%20write%20out%20your%20reasoning.%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ESonia%20Jhas%20is%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FhxKADRl8nGo%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ETEDx%20speaker%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20author%20from%20Toronto%20who%20coaches%20people%20on%20wellness%2C%20self-esteem%2C%20productivity%2C%20purpose%2C%20and%20perseverance.%20Before%20realizing%20her%20desire%20to%20become%20a%20speaker%20and%20author%2C%20she%20was%20a%20client%20manager%20at%20IBM.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20found%20in%20her%20own%20experience%20and%20through%20working%20with%20clients%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-years-resolutions-failure-advice-jonathan-alpert-2018-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ENew%20Year's%20resolutions%20fail%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20when%20people%20set%20goals%20that%20look%20good%20on%20paper%20but%20don't%20align%20with%20their%20reality.%20She%20helps%20her%20clients%20set%20realistic%2C%20sustainable%2C%20and%20measurable%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnew-years-resolutions-couples-maintain-strong-marriage-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eresolutions%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225120%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22headshot%20of%20Sonia%20Jhas%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F658ddb5cec62ab5daf7f5b8a%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223840%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESonia%20Jhas%20helps%20her%20clients%20set%20New%20Year's%20resolutions.%3Cp%3EGooseberry%20Studios%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20her%20strategies%20for%20stopping%20the%20excuses%20and%20procrastination%20and%20accomplishing%20your%20goals%20in%20the%20coming%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELet%20go%20of%20an%20idealized%20version%20of%20your%20future%20self%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20first%20step%20to%20making%20changes%20that%20stick%20is%20letting%20go%20of%20the%20idea%20that%20a%20future%20version%20of%20yourself%20will%20figure%20it%20out%20and%20start%20making%20positive%20changes%20based%20on%20where%20you%20are%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAll%20my%20life%2C%20I%20lived%20with%20this%20idea%20that%20future%20Sonia%20wasn't%20going%20to%20suffer%20in%20the%20ways%20current%20Sonia%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20Jhas%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BI%20thought%20future%20Sonia%20was%20going%20to%20find%20a%20way%20to%20have%20more%20commitment%2C%20more%20resilience%20%E2%80%94%20I%20told%20myself%20she%20isn't%20even%20going%20to%20want%20doughnuts.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20even%20more%20unproductive%20to%20lean%20into%20bad%20habits%20today%20in%20anticipation%20of%20your%20future%20self%20behaving%20perfectly%20tomorrow%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20that's%20eating%20all%20the%20cookies%20or%20lounging%20around%20all%20day.%20This%20form%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fmain-types-of-procrastinators-how-to-avoid-accountability-coaches%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eprocrastination%3C%2Fa%3E%20pushes%20responsibility%20onto%20an%20imagined%2C%20future%20version%20of%20a%20better%20self%20who%20may%20never%20exist.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20so%20long%20I%20was%20filled%20with%20this%20longing%20and%20desire%20to%20arrive%20at%20this%20place%20where%20the%20whole%20Rubik's%20Cube%20would%20line%20up%20the%20way%20it's%20supposed%20to%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20realized%20time%20and%20time%20again%20that%20there's%20no%20magic%20mindset%20fix%20%E2%80%94%20whether%20it's%20January%201%2C%20January%203%2C%20or%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-do-dry-january-sobriety-tips-advice-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EDry%20January%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20or%20any%20other%20version%20of%20that%20perfect%20start%20date.%26quot%3B%20It's%20best%20to%20start%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStop%20searching%20for%20a%20quick%20fix%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJhas%20advises%20against%20believing%20that%20happiness%20is%20just%20one%20push%20of%20hard%20work%20away%20and%20instead%20encourages%20her%20clients%20to%20commit%20to%20long-term%20mindset%20changes.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20believe%20so%20deeply%20that%20happiness%20is%20just%2010%20pounds%20away%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BWe%20want%20to%20sprint%20and%20get%20there%20as%20fast%20as%20we%20can%20because%20we%20think%20then%20we'll%20be%20happy%2C%20and%20we'll%20be%20able%20to%20slow%20down%20and%20take%20a%20breath.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJhas%20finds%20that%20linking%20happiness%20to%20achievement%20makes%20us%20feel%20unfulfilled%20and%20causes%20the%20%26quot%3Bwins%26quot%3B%20to%20feel%20anticlimactic.%20Instead%2C%20she%20advises%20her%20clients%20to%20allow%20themselves%20the%20freedom%20to%20be%20enough%20while%20still%20making%20progress.%20She%20also%20cautions%20against%20forcing%20ourselves%20into%20a%20%26quot%3Brobot%20mode%26quot%3B%20that%20will%20push%20us%20toward%20our%20goals.%20Instead%2C%20address%20the%20%26quot%3Bwhy%26quot%3B%20behind%20your%20desires%20and%20be%20intentional.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBefore%20jumping%20headfirst%20into%20your%20goals%20for%20the%20New%20Year%2C%20she%20suggests%20taking%20stock%20of%20your%20values%20and%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbiggest-mistake-setting-new-years-resolutions-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehow%20they%20align%20with%20your%20goals%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20even%20if%20the%20exploration%20takes%20all%20of%20January.%20Ensure%20that%20your%20goals%20are%20yours%2C%20not%20those%20set%20by%20friends%20or%20family.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20grew%20up%20in%20a%20household%20where%20I%20was%20heavily%20kneaded%20into%20being%20the%20perfect%20version%20of%20who%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20supposed%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BI%20had%20no%20idea%20where%20my%20parents%20stopped%20and%20where%20I%20started.%20It%20led%20to%20an%20early%20midlife%20crisis%20at%2025%20where%20I%20was%20like%2C%20'I%20actually%20don't%20want%20to%20do%20this.'%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20determine%20if%20your%20goals%20and%20values%20are%20truly%20your%20own%2C%20she%20recommends%20journaling%2C%20seeking%20feedback%20from%20trusted%20friends%20or%20professionals%2C%20and%20practicing%20awareness%20through%20meditation%2C%20breathwork%2C%20and%20other%20mindfulness%20practices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ECreate%20a%20mindset%20manifesto%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EOnce%20you%20identify%20your%20goals%2C%20evaluate%20your%20tactics%20to%20reach%20them%20and%20create%20what%20Jhas%20calls%20a%20%26quot%3Bmindset%20manifesto.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20me%2C%20it%20serves%20the%20same%20purpose%20as%20a%20vision%20board%2C%20where%20you're%20thinking%20about%20what%20you%20want%20your%20future%20self%20to%20experience.%20Drop%20into%20an%20aligned%20place%20where%20you%20can%20picture%20your%20day%20%E2%80%94%20maybe%20it's%20'I%20wake%20up%20in%20the%20morning%2C%20my%20feet%20touch%20the%20ground%2C%20and%20I%20reach%20for%20a%20glass%20of%20water%E2%80%A6'%20The%20visualization%20of%20it%20allows%20you%20to%20be%20the%20main%20character%20in%20your%20movie.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThen%20write%20down%20whatever%20best%20captures%20the%20feeling%20you%20want%20to%20experience%2C%20whether%20it's%20a%20statement%2C%20keywords%2C%20or%20an%20in-depth%20diary%20entry.%20Jhas%20advises%20her%20clients%20to%20keep%20it%20on%20their%20phones%20and%20use%20it%20to%20remember%20their%20goals%20and%20their%20%26quot%3Bwhy.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20a%20functional%20model%20to%20feed%20decisions%20through%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%20%26quot%3BHow%20else%20are%20you%20making%20decisions%3F%20Are%20you%20hoping%20you're%20just%20not%20going%20to%20want%20a%20doughnut%3F%20Or%20that%20you'll%20want%20to%20go%20to%20the%20gym%20when%20it's%20dark%20at%204%20p.m.%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EStart%20small%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJhas%20advises%20incorporating%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fstrategies-methods-ways-build-better-habits-new-year-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esmall%2C%20failproof%20habits%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20such%20as%20waking%20up%20and%20doing%20one%20minute%20of%20breathwork%20or%2010%20minutes%20of%20stretching%20%E2%80%94%20into%20your%20routine%20to%20create%20a%20mindset%20shift%20and%20build%20momentum.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou're%20going%20to%20move%20at%20your%20own%20pace%20when%20you're%20connected%20to%20who%20you%20are%2C%20and%20then%20momentum%20builds%2C%20but%20not%20to%20a%20climax%20where%20you're%20going%20to%20fall%20off%20a%20cliff.%20It%20builds%2C%20and%20then%20it%20may%20slow%20down%2C%20but%20you'll%20build%20again%20without%20falling%20off%20the%20wagon%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20Jhas%2C%20this%20also%20requires%20self-trust%20and%20control%2C%20knowing%20that%20if%20you%20snooze%20one%20morning%20because%20your%20body%20needs%20extra%20rest%2C%20it's%20not%20falling%20off%20the%20cliff%3B%20it's%20being%20in%20tune%20with%20yourself%20and%20knowing%20you'll%20give%20yourself%20what%20you%20need%20to%20reach%20your%20goals%20the%20next%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-to-stop-procrastinating-accomplish-new-years-resolutions-goals-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704103802000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65