five%20metres%20was%20expected%20to%20arrive%20in%20Noto%20in%20the%20same%20region%2C%20the%20Japan%20Meterological%20Agency%20(JMA)%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20JMA%20said%20the%20Noto%20region%2C%20on%20the%20Sea%20of%20Japan%20side%20of%20Japan's%20main%20island%20of%20Honshu%2C%20experienced%20a%20rapid%20succession%20of%20quakes%2C%20starting%20with%20a%205.7%20magnitude%20tremor%20at%204%3A06%20pm%20local%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20followed%20by%20a%207.6-magnitude%20quake%20at%204%3A10%20pm%2C%20a%206.1%20magnitude%20quake%20at%204%3A18%20pm%2C%20a%204.5%20magnitude%20one%20at%204%3A23%20pm%2C%20a%204.6%20magnitude%20quake%20at%204%3A29%20pm%2C%20and%204.8%20magnitude%20quake%20at%204%3A32%20pm.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20quake%20with%20a%20magnitude%20of%206.2%20hit%20soon%20after%2C%20the%20US%20Geological%20Survey%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20largest%20of%20the%20quakes%20prompted%20broadcasters%20to%20switch%20to%20special%20programming%20and%20make%20urgent%20calls%20for%20affected%20residents%20to%20leave%20for%20higher%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20realise%20your%20home%2C%20your%20belongings%20are%20all%20precious%20to%20you%2C%20but%20your%20lives%20are%20important%20above%20everything%20else.%20Run%20to%20the%20highest%20ground%20possible%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20presenter%20on%20broadcaster%20NHK%20told%20viewers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJapan%20has%20strict%20construction%20regulations%20intended%20to%20ensure%20buildings%20can%20withstand%20strong%20earthquakes%20and%20routinely%20holds%20emergency%20drills%20to%20prepare%20for%20a%20major%20jolt.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20country%20is%20haunted%20by%20the%20memory%20of%20a%20massive%209.0-magnitude%20undersea%20quake%20off%20northeastern%20Japan%20in%20March%202011%2C%20which%20triggered%20a%20tsunami%20that%20left%20around%2018%2C500%20people%20dead%20or%20missing.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%202011%20tsunami%20also%20sent%20three%20reactors%20into%20meltdown%20at%20the%20Fukushima%20nuclear%20plant%2C%20causing%20Japan's%20worst%20post-war%20disaster%20and%20the%20most%20serious%20nuclear%20accident%20since%20Chernobyl.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20March%202022%2C%20a%207.4-magnitude%20quake%20off%20the%20coast%20of%20Fukushima%20shook%20large%20areas%20of%20eastern%20Japan%2C%20killing%20three%20people.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20capital%20Tokyo%20was%20devastated%20by%20a%20huge%20earthquake%20a%20century%20ago%20in%201923.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704103380000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-01%2F802va8s8_tokyo-generic-unsplash_625x300_03_January_23.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffirst-tsunami-waves-hit-japan-after-7-5-quake-5-metre-waves-expected-too-4780007%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20powerful%207.5%20earthquake%20hit%20central%20Japan%20on%20Monday%2C%20the%20USGS%20said%2C%20prompting%20tsunami%20warnings%20and%20authorities%20to%20urge%20people%20in%20the%20area%20to%20move%20to%20higher%20ground.%26quot%3BAll%20residents%20must%20evacuate%20immediately%20to%20higher%20ground%2C%26quot%3B%20national%20broadcaster%20said%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffirst-tsunami-waves-hit-japan-after-7-5-quake-5-metre-waves-expected-too-4780007%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffirst-tsunami-waves-hit-japan-after-7-5-quake-5-metre-waves-expected-too-4780007%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Ffirst-tsunami-waves-hit-japan-after-7-5-quake-5-metre-waves-expected-too-4780007%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22How%20to%20check%20Uber%20rating%3B%20why%20it's%20important%20in%20booking%20cab%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704103372000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106452241%2Cimgsize-14110.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fgadgets-news%2Fhow-to-check-your-uber-rating-and-why-it-can-be-important-in-booking-a-cab%2Farticleshow%2F106452259.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22This%20article%20discusses%20how%20Uber%20users%20can%20check%20their%20passenger%20ratings%20in%20the%20app's%20Privacy%20Center.%20Users%20can%20view%20a%20breakdown%20of%20their%20average%20rating%2C%20including%20the%20number%20of%205-star%20and%201-star%20ratings.%20The%20article%20also%20mentions%20that%20drivers%20often%20check%20passenger%20ratings%20before%20accepting%20trips.%20It%20provides%20tips%20on%20how%20to%20improve%20your%20rating%2C%20such%20as%20taking%20your%20belongings%20with%20you%2C%20being%20ready%20to%20go%20when%20the%20driver%20arrives%2C%20and%20treating%20drivers%20with%20respect.%20The%20Privacy%20Center%20also%20allows%20users%20to%20review%20their%20past%20trip%20information%2C%20payment%20details%2C%20and%20control%20marketing%20preferences.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TIMESOFINDIA.COM%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%E2%80%99s%20Housing%20Boom%20Calls%20for%20Urgent%20Upgrade%20in%20Construction%20Practices%2C%20Labour%20Rights%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16134843%2Fimage-1392.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20developers%E2%80%99%20decision%20to%20demolish%20the%20multi-storey%20towers%20at%20the%20Chintels%20Paradiso%20Housing%20complex%20in%20Gurgaon%20and%20in%20the%20Delhi%20Development%20Authority%E2%80%99s%20(DDA%E2%80%99s)%20Signature%20View%20Apartments%20in%20North%20Delhi%E2%80%99s%20Mukherjee%20Nagar%20draws%20serious%20attention%20to%20the%20unfortunate%20state%20of%20the%20construction%20industry%20in%20India%20today.%20The%20newly%20built%20apartment%20structures%20have%20to%20be%20pulled%20down%20because%20of%20poor%20construction%20putting%20occupants%20lives%20at%20risk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20proposal%20to%20demolish%20houses%20in%20both%20residential%20complexes%20has%20caused%20widespread%20concern%20amongst%20home%20buyers%20in%20the%20in%20and%20around%20Delhi.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EPeople%20who%20had%20invested%20their%20savings%20to%20buy%20a%20home%20that%20they%20intended%20to%20live%20in%20are%20not%20only%20sorely%20disappointed%2C%20but%20also%20angry%20at%20having%20waited%20for%20years%20to%20move%20into%20their%20apartments%20and%20then%20have%20their%20dreams%20shattered%20as%20their%20newly%20built%20apartments%20have%20to%20be%20evacuated%20and%20demolished.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBecause%20of%20poor%20construction%2C%20chunks%20of%20plaster%20had%20begun%20to%20fall%20in%20different%20parts%20of%20the%20DDA%20apartments%20while%20in%20the%20case%20of%20Chintels%20Paradiso%2C%20in%20one%20of%20the%20apartment%20blocks%2C%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20sixth%20floor%20had%20fallen%20down%20all%20the%20way%20to%20the%20first%20floor%2C%20killing%20two%20women%20residents%20and%20injuring%20a%20man.%20Home%20owners%20in%20both%20complexes%20now%20have%20to%20wait%20as%20the%20developers%20proceed%20to%20demolish%20the%20constructed%20buildings%2C%20and%20then%20go%20through%20the%20process%20of%20reconstructing%20them.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResidents%20have%20been%20promised%20rental%20compensation%20until%20they%20are%20given%20possession%20of%20the%20newly%20constructed%20apartments.%20The%20terms%20offered%20by%20the%20two%20developers%2C%20DDA%20and%20Chintels%2C%20vary.%20The%20DDA%20is%20offering%20owners%20an%20added%20increase%20of%20around%2020%20sq.%20ft.%20in%20the%20balcony%20area%20of%20each%20apartment%20at%20a%20marginal%20increase%20in%20cost%20and%20some%20additional%20common%20facilities%2C%20whereas%20Chintels%E2%80%99%20offer%20has%20not%20seen%20any%20change.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOwners%20have%20accepted%20the%20proposal%20to%20rebuild%20the%20houses%20in%20both%20cases%20as%20the%20alternative%20of%20accepting%20a%20cash%20settlement%20would%20be%20on%20the%20basis%20of%20the%20cost%20of%20construction%20at%20the%20time%20of%20original%20sale%20which%20is%20much%20lower%20in%20comparison%20to%20the%20cost%20of%20construction%20today%20and%20is%20not%20acceptable%20to%20most%20owners.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20DDA%20started%20construction%20of%20the%2012%20apartment%20towers%20consisting%20of%20336%20residential%20units%20in%202007%20and%20completed%20them%20in%202011.%20Soon%20after%20taking%20possession%20in%202012%2C%20owners%20noticed%20minor%20cracks%20and%20structural%20defects%20appearing%20in%20the%20buildings.%20The%20first%20allottee%20entered%20his%20home%20to%20find%20that%20a%20part%20of%20the%20roof%20had%20caved%20in.%20Subsequently%2C%20ceiling%20plaster%20falling%20and%20cracks%20in%20beams%20and%20balconies%20was%20reported%20in%2026%20flats.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fvideo-santosh-mehrotra-unemployment-unpaid-worker%5C%22%3EWatch%20%7C%20What%20India%E2%80%99s%20Growing%20Army%20of%20Unpaid%20Workers%20Means%20for%20It%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EResidents%20raised%20these%20issues%20with%20the%20DDA%20but%20received%20no%20positive%20response.%20In%20June%202022%2C%20DDA%20asked%20IIT%20Delhi%20and%20Shriram%20Laboratories%20to%20test%20the%20structural%20integrity%20of%20the%20buildings.%20IIT%20submitted%20their%20report%20in%20November%202022%20declaring%20the%20buildings%20unfit%20for%20occupation.%20The%20Residents%20Welfare%20Association%20(RWA)%20negotiated%20the%20matter%20with%20DDA%20and%20settled%20for%20evacuation%20and%20demolition%20of%20all%20structures%20to%20be%20followed%20by%20new%20construction%20of%20the%20flats%20exactly%20as%20they%20were%20before%20along%20with%20the%20addition%20of%20144%20high%20income%20group%20(HIG)%20flats%2C%20168%20economically%20weaker%20section%20(EWS)%20flats%20as%20well%20as%20a%20clubhouse%20and%20community%20centre.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EChintels%20Paradiso%20in%20Gurgaon%20consisting%20of%20nine%2C%2014%20storey%20towers%20each%20with%2060%20apartments%20was%20completed%20in%20two%20phases%20in%202016%20and%20in%202017.%20After%20the%20first%20few%20residents%20moved%20in%2C%20they%20observed%20structural%20issues%2C%20cracks%20in%20ceilings%20and%20balconies%2C%20tiles%20falling%20off%2C%20and%20deflection%20in%20some%20balconies.%20After%20a%20structural%20audit%20by%20IIT%2C%20two%20towers%20were%20declared%20unfit%20for%20occupation.%20In%20July%202021%2C%20in%20Tower%20H%E2%80%99s%20front%20lobby%2C%20a%20portion%20of%20the%20ceiling%20fell%20down.%20On%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3E%20February%2010%2C%202022%2C%20the%20ceiling%20slab%20on%20the%20sixth%20floor%20of%20Tower%20D%20collapsed%20and%20fell%20all%20the%20way%20down%20to%20the%20first%20floor%20killing%20two%20women%20and%20injuring%20one%20man.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20IIT%20report%20clearly%20stated%20that%20the%20towers%20were%20not%20safe%20for%20habitation%20because%20of%20the%20high%20chloride%20content%20in%20the%20concrete%20which%20caused%20corrosion%20of%20the%20steel%20bars%20and%20that%20all%20flats%20be%20vacated%20and%20demolished.%20Between%20April-July%202023%2C%20the%20builder%20provided%20two%20options%20to%20the%20affected%20residents%20%E2%80%93%20either%20buy%20back%20or%20accept%20total%20reconstruction%20of%20all%20apartment%20blocks.%20The%20offer%20to%20reconstruct%20was%20accepted.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWho%20is%20responsible%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20worth%20exploring%20what%20really%20happened%20in%20terms%20of%20shortcomings%20in%20both%20these%20projects.%20How%20is%20it%20that%20the%20developers%20were%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20architects%20and%20structural%20engineers%20were%20not%20effectively%20involved%20in%20the%20process%20of%20implementing%20the%20project%3F%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20accordance%20with%20their%20professional%20commitment%2C%20they%20were%20required%20to%20not%20only%20provide%20the%20necessary%20drawings%20and%20details%20but%20also%20systematically%20oversee%20the%20actual%20construction%20on%20a%20timely%20basis.%20Did%20the%20failures%20occur%20only%20because%20of%20faulty%20implementation%20on%20the%20part%20of%20the%20contractors%20responsible%20for%20the%20construction%3F%20To%20some%20extent%2C%20the%20responsibility%20falls%20on%20all%20the%20professionals%20involved.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAs%20unskilled%20labour%20forms%20a%20large%20part%20of%20the%20construction%20team%2C%20close%20monitoring%20of%20the%20implementation%20process%20by%20the%20supervisory%20staff%20is%20of%20prime%20importance.%20Although%20the%20volume%20of%20construction%20work%20has%20been%20steadily%20increasing%20across%20the%20country%20since%20the%20mid-1970s%2C%20the%20training%20of%20skilled%20craftsmen%20for%20construction%20work%20is%20inadequate%20and%20has%20not%20kept%20pace.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWhile%20architects%20and%20structural%20engineers%20are%20mainly%20responsible%20for%20producing%20the%20necessary%20drawings%2C%20specifications%2C%20and%20bill%20of%20quantities%20relating%20to%20their%20projects%2C%20they%20also%20need%20to%20check%20the%20progress%20of%20construction%20at%20different%20stages%20to%20ensure%20that%20work%20is%20being%20implemented%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20plans.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20984px)%2061vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2045vw%2C%20600px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23103952%2F3158023774_54f2900169_c.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22799%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23103952%2F3158023774_54f2900169_c.jpg%20799w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F07%2F23103952%2F3158023774_54f2900169_c-300x241.jpg%20300w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-664608%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22641%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Most%20of%20this%20so-called%20increase%20in%20%E2%80%98jobs%E2%80%99%20in%20agriculture%20since%202019%20is%20in%20%E2%80%98unpaid%20family%20labour%E2%80%99%2C%20a%20form%20of%20self-employment%20where%20women%2C%20youth%20and%20children%20join%20other%20family%20members%20to%20appear%20%E2%80%98employed%E2%80%99.%E2%80%99%20Photo%3A%20jasleen_kaur%2FFlickr%20(CC%20BY-SA%202.0)%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20the%20case%20of%20the%20aforementioned%20housing%20projects%2C%20it%20is%20quite%20clear%20that%20there%20were%20serious%20defaults%20in%20ensuring%20that%20specifications%20and%20drawing%20details%20were%20properly%20implemented.%20To%20some%20extent%2C%20this%20is%20because%20architects%20and%20engineers%20are%20generally%20paid%20fees%20that%20barely%20cover%20their%20cost%20as%20a%20result%20of%20which%20they%20tend%20to%20cut%20corners.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EDDA%20and%20other%20government%20agencies%20make%20a%20provision%20of%2010%25%20or%20more%20to%20cover%20their%20in-house%20design%20and%20engineering%20costs%2C%20but%20when%20it%20comes%20to%20architect%E2%80%99s%20and%20engineer%E2%80%99s%20fees%2C%20they%20generally%20pay%203%25%20to%204%25%20or%20even%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20building%20industry%20happens%20to%20be%20one%20of%20the%20largest%20employers%20of%20workers%20in%20the%20informal%20sector.%20The%20average%20cost%20of%20construction%20in%20India%20is%20one%20of%20the%20lowest%20in%20the%20world.%20This%20is%20largely%20due%20to%20the%20small%20component%20allocated%20to%20labour%20in%20the%20total%20building%20cost.%20If%20building%20skills%20are%20to%20be%20improved%2C%20the%20cost%20of%20all%20labour%20will%20need%20to%20be%20substantially%20increased%2C%20along%20with%20a%20focussed%20increase%20in%20the%20process%20of%20training%20craftsmen%20all%20over%20the%20country.%20This%20can%20only%20happen%20if%2C%20in%20addition%20to%20setting%20up%20a%20large%20number%20of%20craft%20training%20institutes%20in%20every%20state%2C%20construction%20contractors%20implementing%20projects%20above%20a%20certain%20size%20were%20required%2C%20by%20law%2C%20to%20set%20up%20necessary%20skill%20training%20camps%20at%20their%20building%20sites.%20They%20should%20also%20be%20required%20to%20employ%20a%20specific%20number%20of%20such%20trained%20craftsmen.%20The%20enforcement%20of%20such%20training%20programs%20will%20increase%20the%20number%20of%20trained%20craftsmen%20all%20across%20the%20country.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBuilders%2C%20who%20make%20the%20maximum%20profit%20from%20these%2C%20should%20be%20made%20directly%20responsible%20not%20only%20for%20developing%20skills%20but%20also%20to%20ensure%20safe%20conditions%20on%20building%20sites.%20They%20need%20to%20shift%20to%20updated%20construction%20methods%20along%20with%20ensuring%20job%20security%20for%20all%20workers.%20The%20system%20of%20daily%20wage%20labour%20being%20supplied%20by%20middlemen%20who%20do%20not%20really%20protect%20the%20workers%E2%80%99%20long-term%20interests%20needs%20to%20be%20done%20away%20with.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EConstruction%20industry%20needs%20a%20complete%20overhaul%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EDespite%20the%20fact%20that%20the%20building%20industry%20has%20steadily%20grown%20over%20the%20years%20with%20more%20and%20more%20construction%20due%20to%20industrial%20growth%20and%20urban%20development%2C%20actual%20conditions%20on%20many%20building%20sites%20remain%20unsafe%20and%20primitive.%20It%20is%20common%20to%20see%20bamboo%20or%20wooden%20%3Cem%3Eballi%3C%2Fem%3E%20scaffolding%2C%20along%20with%20wooden%20ramps%2C%20tied%20together%20with%20ropes.%20Workers%20on%20such%20sites%2C%20including%20women%2C%20work%20without%20proper%20safety%20gear%20and%20harness%20and%20carry%20building%20materials%20like%20bricks%20and%20concrete%20on%20their%20heads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccidents%20are%20frequent%20and%20workers%E2%80%99%20lives%20are%20at%20risk.%20But%20in%20the%20absence%20of%20any%20control%2C%20and%20because%20this%20system%20is%20cheap%2C%20contractors%20continue%20to%20avoid%20upgrading%20to%20save%20expense.%20This%20is%20a%20dangerous%20system%20that%20needs%20complete%20overhaul.%20This%20is%20possible%2C%20both%2C%20by%20the%20enactment%20of%20stringent%20laws%20as%20well%20as%20by%20training%20large%20numbers%20of%20skilled%20workers.%20The%20use%20of%20unskilled%20workers%20needs%20to%20be%20steadily%20reduced%2C%20and%20ultimately%20done%20away%20with%20completely%20across%20the%20nation.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fmgnregs-aadhaar-system-payment%5C%22%3EAll%20MGNREGS%20Wages%20to%20Be%20Paid%20Through%20Aadhaar-Linked%20System%20From%20Today%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EWith%20the%20level%20of%20construction%20skills%20currently%20available%2C%20most%20contractors%20are%20only%20equipped%20to%20safely%20build%20ground%20plus%20two%20floors%20in%20most%20parts%20of%20the%20country.%20In%20the%20present%20situation%2C%20for%20all%20buildings%20that%20are%20higher%20than%20that%2C%20we%20are%20taking%20a%20serious%20risk%20by%20building%20unsafe%20structures.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIn%20all%20construction%20work%2C%20the%20use%20of%20tubular%20steel%20scaffolding%20properly%20bolted%20together%20along%20with%20mechanical%20hoists%20and%20lifts%20for%20vertical%20movement%20of%20crew%20and%20material%20must%20be%20made%20compulsory.%20Concrete%20mixers%20with%20flexible%20pipes%20for%20delivery%20of%20mixed%20concrete%20is%20also%20necessary.%20Safety%20conditions%20with%20the%20proper%20enclosure%20of%20all%20buildings%20under%20construction%20must%20be%20ensured.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EFor%20the%20implementation%20of%20such%20proposals%20all%20workers%20need%20to%20be%20trained.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20traditional%20skills%20related%20to%20carpentry%2C%20woodwork%2C%20cutting%2C%20polishing%20and%20installation%20of%20stonework%2C%20welding%20of%20steel%2C%20etc.%20along%20with%20the%20use%20of%20new%20machines%20and%20improved%20tools%20need%20to%20be%20taught%20and%20implemented%20with%20short%20term%20courses.%20Needless%20to%20say%2C%20all%20workers%20on%20building%20sites%20should%20also%20be%20provided%20with%20proper%20uniforms%20and%20safety%20gear%20without%20which%20they%20should%20not%20be%20permitted%20on%20building%20sites.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EOne%20of%20the%20important%20aspects%20of%20improving%20building%20techniques%20is%20the%20need%20to%20train%20workmen%20and%20engineers%20in%20project%20management.%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20involves%20proper%20coordination%20of%20different%20craft%20skills%20to%20ensure%20overall%20time%20and%20cost%20control%20with%20the%20help%20of%20pert%20charts%2C%20and%20the%20regular%20checking%20and%20upgrading%20of%20the%20different%20aspects%20of%20work%20on%20all%20building%20sites.%20Proper%20project%20management%20ultimately%20results%20in%20better%20construction%20at%20cheaper%20costs.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt%20is%20also%20important%20to%20ensure%20the%20provision%20of%20proper%20living%20accommodation%20for%20workers%20when%20construction%20sites%20are%20far%20from%20the%20villages%20or%20the%20area%20where%20the%20construction%20crew%20lives.%20In%20all%20large-scale%20development%20projects%2C%20a%20separate%20area%20should%20be%20allocated%20for%20building%20a%20complex%20of%20affordable%20dwelling%20units%20in%20close%20proximity.%20In%20order%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20needs%20of%20skilled%20and%20unskilled%20workers%20and%20their%20families%20are%20taken%20care%20of%2C%20the%20entire%20complex%20along%20with%20community%20support%20facilities%20should%20be%20financed%20and%20maintained%20by%20the%20builders%20along%20with%20the%20provision%20of%20safe%20transportation%20to%20individual%20building%20sites.%20Support%20facilities%20like%20schools%2C%20health%20centres%20and%20informal%20sector%20shopping%20complexes%20should%20all%20be%20part%20of%20such%20organised%20low-income%20settlement.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cins%3EAlso%20read%3A%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fwhy-development-of-skill-centres-is-essential-for-rural-development%5C%22%3E%20Why%20Development%20of%20Skill%20Centres%20Is%20Essential%20For%20Rural%20Development%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fins%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20proposal%20to%20provide%20living%20accommodation%20for%20workers%20on%20building%20sites%20is%20not%20new.%20This%20was%20a%20standard%20requirement%20of%20all%20large%20projects%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20during%20the%20construction%20boom%20in%20the%201960s.%20All%20contractors%20had%20to%20provide%20proper%20living%20and%20support%20facilities%20for%20all%20the%20labour%20that%20they%20brought%20from%20overseas%20for%20construction%20projects.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20miserable%20conditions%20on%20most%20of%20our%20construction%20sites%20along%20with%20the%20exploitation%20of%20labour%20throughout%20the%20country%20continues%20unabated%20because%20of%20lack%20of%20government%20intervention%20and%20control.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EContractors%20must%20also%20be%20made%20responsible%20for%20the%20provision%20of%20crafts%20and%20skill%20training%20institutes%20which%20would%20provide%20training%20in%20construction%20related%20skills%2C%20along%20with%20separate%20courses%20or%20advanced%20training%20in%20IT-related%20construction%20systems.%20These%20should%20be%20permanent%20educational%20institutes%2C%20which%20would%20periodically%20be%20upgraded%20in%20relation%20to%20the%20latest%20available%20construction%20technology.%20Such%20crafts%20and%20skill%20training%20institutes%20may%20over%20time%20become%20self-supporting%2C%20maintaining%20a%20close%20link%20with%20the%20building%20industry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EA%20number%20of%20such%20institutions%20located%20in%20the%20rural%20areas%20of%20each%20state%20would%20help%20to%20not%20only%20provide%20employment%2C%20but%20also%20ensure%20proper%20and%20systematic%20development%20of%20all%20rural%20areas%20on%20a%20continuing%20basis%20in%20the%20future.%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAccording%20to%20GDP%20data%2C%20India%20is%20currently%20one%20of%20the%20world%E2%80%99s%20fastest%20growing%20major%20economies%20and%20is%20currently%20in%20the%20middle%20of%20a%20housing%20boom.%20The%20demand%20for%20housing%20is%20steadily%20increasing%20in%20most%20urban%20areas%20and%20is%20expected%20to%20grow%20even%20faster%20in%20the%20years%20ahead.%20The%20long-awaited%20boom%20has%20created%20millions%20of%20new%20jobs.%20This%20has%20come%20after%20six%20years%20of%20debt%20and%20pandemic-induced%20downturn%20before%20the%20construction%20sector%20began%20improving%20last%20year.%20It%20has%20been%20driven%20by%20a%20severe%20housing%20shortage%20in%20big%20cities%20along%20with%20strong%20population%20growth.%20Steadily%20rising%20incomes%20has%20also%20been%20responsible%20for%20the%20increase%20in%20housing%20demand.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAcross%20the%20country%20there%20was%20an%20urban%20housing%20shortage%20of%2019%20million%20housing%20units%20last%20year.%20According%20to%20government%20estimates%20this%20is%20expected%20to%20double%20by%202030.%20The%20construction%20sector%20has%20contributed%20significantly%20to%20economic%20growth%20and%20this%20is%20likely%20to%20continue%20over%20the%20next%20couple%20of%20years.%20As%20per%20some%20real%20estate%20consultants%2C%20despite%20an%20increase%20in%20prices%2C%20home%20sales%20in%20seven%20largest%20cities%20increased%20by%20over%2036%25%20over%20the%20last%20quarter.%20With%20this%20increased%20housing%20demand%2C%20this%20is%20the%20right%20time%20for%20the%20government%20to%20take%20steps%20to%20improve%20the%20quality%20of%20construction%20across%20the%20country.%20Improved%20construction%20quality%20will%20automatically%20lead%20to%20an%20increase%20in%20wages%20of%20construction%20workers%20along%20with%20a%20substantial%20increase%20in%20the%20size%20of%20the%20construction%20industry.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fauthor%2Franjitsibikhi%5C%22%3ERanjit%20Sabikhi%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20an%20architect%20and%20urban%20designer.%20He%20was%20formerly%20a%20Professor%20of%20Urban%20Design%20at%20the%20School%20of%20Planning%20and%20Architecture%2C%20Delhi.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704103213000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F10%2F16134843%2Fimage-1392.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Findias-housing-boom-calls-for-urgent-upgrade-in-construction-practices-labour-rights%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20miserable%20conditions%20on%20most%20of%20our%20construction%20sites%20along%20with%20the%20exploitation%20of%20labour%20throughout