0cracks%20in%20roads%2C%20subway%20trains%20shaking%20and%20buildings%20collapsing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20agency%20added%20there%20is%20a%2010%20to%2020%25%20chance%20more%20earthquakes%20of%20similar%20magnitude%20could%20hit%20within%20the%20next%20few%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Japan%20Meteorological%20Agency%20issued%20a%20%26quot%3Bmajor%20tsunami%20warning%26quot%3B%20for%20Noto%2C%20Ishikawa%20Prefecture%2C%20warning%20of%20waves%20as%20high%20as%2016%20feet.%20Tsunami%20warnings%20were%20also%20issued%20for%20the%20neighboring%20Niigata%20and%20Toyama%20prefectures%2C%20where%20waves%20are%20expected%20to%20reach%20nearly%2010%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222412%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20map%20shows%20tsunami%20warnings%20in%20effect%20in%20Japan%20on%20Jan%201%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65927fefab6f2ebb11f7ff66%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221266%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ETsunami%20warnings%20are%20in%20effect%20as%20of%2017%3A43%20local%20time%20(3%3A43%E2%80%AFAM%20ET)%20on%20January%201%2C%202024.%3Cp%3EJapan%20Meteorological%20Center%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20the%20first%20time%20such%20warnings%20have%20been%20issued%20since%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-show-damage-of-japans-2011-disaster-2016-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2011%20tsunami%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20hit%20Japan%20following%20a%209.0%20magnitude%20earthquake%2C%20causing%20the%20Fukushima%20Daiichi%20nuclear%20disaster%20and%20the%20death%20of%20more%20than%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22%20nofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.latimes.com%2Fworld%2Fasia%2Fla-fg-fukushima-nuclear-cleanup-20150311-story.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3E18%2C000%20people.%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWaves%20during%20the%202011%20tsunami%20reached%20heights%20up%20to%20almost%20130%20feet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGovernment%20spokesman%