ahrenheit%2C%20NKH%20TV%20reported.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESix%20people%20are%20thought%20to%20be%20stuck%20under%20rubble%20in%20collapsed%20houses%20on%20the%20Noto%20Peninsula%2C%20and%20no%20information%20has%20been%20released%20on%20their%20condition%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fworld%2Flive%2F2024%2Fjan%2F01%2Fjapan-tsunami-earthquake-warning-latest-updates-live%23maincontent%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eper%20The%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Multiple%20people%20were%20also%20reported%20to%20be%20trapped%20in%20collapsed%20houses%20in%20Suzu%2C%20Ishikawa%2C%20per%20NHK%20TV.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%2C%20a%20fire%20has%20broken%20out%20in%20Wajima%20City%2C%20per%20The%20Guardian.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESmall%20tsunami%20waves%20are%20common%20and%20cause%20little%20damage%2C%20but%20any%20waves%20with%20runups%20over%20one%20meter%20(3.28%20feet)%20can%20be%20particularly%20dangerous%20to%20people%20living%20near%20coastal%20areas%2C%20per%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.noaa.gov%2Fjetstream%2Ftsunamis%2Ftsunami-dangers%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EUS%20National%20Oceanic%20and%20Atmospheric%20Administration%20website%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20force%20of%20the%20waves%20themselves%20can%20cause%20substantial%20damage%2C%20but%20tsunamis%20are%20also%20dangerous%20because%20they%20cause%20flooding%2C%20erosion%2C%20and%20strong%20currents%20that%20can%20drag%20people%20out%20to%20sea.%20They%20can%20also%20bring%20in%20floating%20debris%20like%20trees%20and%20cars%2C%20that%20can%20act%20like%20battering%20rams%2C%20per%20NOAA.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EThis%20story%20is%20developing.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-braces-16ft-tsunami-after-struck-powerful-earthquakes-waves-wajima-2024-1%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704102497000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F65927f3dec62ab5daf7fd3fe%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-braces-16ft-tsunami-after-struck-powerful-earthquakes-waves-wajima-2024-1%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Japanese%20public%20broadcaster%20NHK%20TV%20urged%20people%20to%20flee%20to%20high%20land%20or%20the%20top%20of%20a%20nearby%20building%20as%20quickly%20as%20possible.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22mguenot%40businessinsider.com%20(Marianne%20Guenot)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A121%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjapan-braces-16ft-tsunami-after-struck-powerful-earthquakes-waves-wajima-2024-1%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Truckers%20Protest%20New%20Law%20That%20Increases%20Jail%20Term%20For%20Road%20Accidents%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20change%20in%20the%20colonial-era%20criminal%20laws%20increasing%20jail%20term%20in%20hit-and-run%20cases%20has%20triggered%20truckers'%20protests%20across%20the%20country.%20Under%20the%20new%20law%2C%20drivers%20can%20be%20jailed%20for%20up%20to%2010%20years%20for%20fleeing%20and%20not%20reporting%20a%20fatal%20accident.%20Earlier%2C%20the%20accused%20could%20be%20jailed%20only%20for%20up%20to%20two%20years%20under%20Section%20304A%20of%20the%20IPC%20(causing%20death%20by%20negligence).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrivate%20bus%20operators%20have%20gone%20on%20strike%20today%20in%20Haryana's%20Jind%20while%20those%20running%20autos%20too%20have%20opened%20a%20new%20front%20against%20the%20new%20law.%C2%A0The%20truckers%20allege%20the%20new%20law%20will%20discourage%20drivers%20from%20their%20duty%20and%20also%20prevent%20new%20ones%20to%20take%20up%20the%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20transporters%20say%20no%20one%20causes%20accidents%20intentionally%20and%20the%20drivers%20fear%20of%20being%20thrashed%20by%20a%20mob%20if%20they%20try%20to%20take%20the%20injured%20to%20hospital%2C%20demanding%20that%20the%20%26quot%3Bblack%20law%26quot%3B%20be%20repealed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThey%20also%20expressed%20fear%20that%20if%20an%20accident%20happens%20due%20to%20the%20fog%2C%20the%20driver%20will%20be%20punished%20for%2010%20years%20without%20any%20fault%20of%20his.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESimilar%20demonstrations%20erupted%20in%20Lucknow%20where%20bus%20drivers%20too%20joined%20the%20truckers%20in%20their%20protest%20against%20the%20new%20law.%20Truck%20and%20tanker%20drivers%20staged%20protests%20in%20parts%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20too.%20Yesterday%2C%20some%20truckers%20had%20blocked%20NH-2%20in%20West%20Bengal's%20Hooghly%20district%20to%20protest%20the%20new%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDrivers%20fear%20being%20roughed%20up%20by%20locals%20after%20accidents%20and%20therefore%2C%20they%20try%20to%20flee%20such%20situations%20without%20reporting%20them%20to%20the%20authorities.%20Lengthy%20procedures%20involving%20the%20police%20are%20another%20reason%20that%20discourage%20them%20to%20take%20the%20legal%20route.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Bharatiya%20Nyaya%20(Second)%20Sanhita%2C%202023%20replaced%20the%20British-era%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20last%20year%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20simplify%20and%20Indianise%20the%20criminal%20laws.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704101880000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fhq2thv7g_truckers-protest-pti_625x300_01_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftruckers-protest-new-law-that-increases-jail-term-for-road-accidents-4779682%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20change%20in%20the%20colonial-era%20criminal%20laws%20increasing%20jail%20term%20in%20hit-and-run%20cases%20has%20triggered%20truckers'%20protests%20across%20the%20country.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftruckers-protest-new-law-that-increases-jail-term-for-road-accidents-4779682%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftruckers-protest-new-law-that-increases-jail-term-for-road-accidents-4779682%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Ftruckers-protest-new-law-that-increases-jail-term-for-road-accidents-4779682%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Total%20of%2021%20quakes%20above%204.0%20magnitude%20hit%20Japan%3A%20Met%20office%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704101787000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106451316%2Cimgsize-1550537.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftotal-of-21-quakes-above-4-0-magnitude-hit-japan-met-office%2Farticleshow%2F106451267.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F106451267.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3E%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftotal-of-21-quakes-above-4-0-magnitude-hit-japan-met-office%2Farticleshow%2F106451267.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm-timesofindia-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftotal-of-21-quakes-above-4-0-magnitude-hit-japan-met-office%2Famp_articleshow%2F106451267.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fm.timesofindia.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Ftotal-of-21-quakes-above-4-0-magnitude-hit-japan-met-office%2Famp_articleshow%2F106451267.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BEven%20Pakistan...%26quot%3B%3A%20Waugh%20Wants%20ICC%2C%20India%20To%20Step%20In%20As%20Teams%20Ignore%20Test%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EFormer%20Australia%20skipper%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Steve%20Waugh%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F441-steve-waugh-playerprofile%5C%22%3ESteve%20Waugh%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20slammed%20the%20International%20Cricket%20Council%20and%20top%20cricket%20boards%2C%20including%20the%20BCCI%2C%20for%20not%20caring%20about%20Test%20cricket%20after%20South%20Africa%20named%20a%20depleted%20red-ball%20squad%20for%20the%20tour%20of%20New%20Zealand%2C%20prioritising%20its%20T20%20league%20over%20the%20longest%20format.%20Cricket%20South%20Africa%20(CSA)%20have%20named%20a%20second-string%20Test%20squad%20which%20has%20seven%20uncapped%20players%2C%20including%20a%20new%20captain%2C%20for%20next%20month's%20two-Test%20series%20against%20New%20Zealand.%20The%20top%20South%20African%20cricketers%20are%20contracted%20to%20play%20in%20the%20second%20season%20of%20the%20SA20%2C%20the%20T20%20league%20launched%20by%20CSA%20and%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20investors%2C%20which%20clashes%20with%20the%20tour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20CSA%20ruling%2C%20no%20player%20contracted%20to%20SA20%20franchises%20is%20eligible%20for%20selection%20for%20the%20Tests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BObviously%2C%20they%20don't%20care.%20It's%20going%20to%20happen%20if%20the%20South%20African%20cricket%20board%20are%20any%20indication%20of%20the%20future%2C%20keeping%20their%20best%20players%20at%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20Waugh%20told%20the%20Sydney%20Morning%20Hearld.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20was%20New%20Zealand%2C%20I%20wouldn't%20even%20play%20the%20series.%20I%20don't%20know%20why%20they're%20even%20playing.%20Why%20would%20you%20when%20it%20shows%20a%20lack%20of%20respect%20for%20New%20Zealand%20cricket%3F%26quot%3B%20Initially%2C%20Waugh%20had%20taken%20to%20Instagram%20to%20raise%20his%20concern.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20this%20a%20defining%20moment%20in%20the%20death%20of%20Test%20cricket%3F%20Surely%20the%20ICC%20along%20(with)%20the%20cricket%20boards%20of%20India%2C%20England%20and%20Australia%20must%20step%20in%20to%20protect%20the%20purest%20form%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHistory%20and%20tradition%20must%20count%20for%20something.%20If%20we%20stand%20by%20and%20allow%20profits%20to%20be%20the%20defining%20criteria%2C%20the%20legacy%20of%20(Sir%20Don)%20Bradman%2C%20(WG)%20Grace%20and%20(Sir%20Garfield)%20Sobers%20will%20be%20irrelevant%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt's%20not%20the%20first%20time%20South%20Africa%20has%20prioritised%20its%20domestic%20T20%20league%20over%20international%20cricket.%20Last%20year%2C%20they%20forfeited%20an%20ODI%20series%20in%20Australia%20to%20have%20their%20best%20players%20feature%20in%20that%20league.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20the%20ICC%20or%20someone%20doesn't%20step%20in%20shortly%20then%20Test%20cricket%20doesn't%20become%20Test%20cricket%20because%20you're%20not%20testing%20yourself%20against%20the%20best%20players.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20understand%20why%20players%20don't%20come.%20They're%20not%20getting%20paid%20properly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20don't%20understand%20why%20ICC%20or%20the%20top%20countries%2C%20who%20are%20making%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%20don't%20just%20have%20a%20regulation%20set%20fee%20for%20Test%20matches%20which%20is%20a%20premium%2C%20so%20people%20are%20incentivised%20to%20play%20Test%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOtherwise%2C%20they%20just%20play%20T10%20or%20T20.%20The%20public%20are%20the%20ones%20who%20are%20going%20to%20suffers%20because%20it's%20not%20the%20full%20side%20playing%2C%20so%20it's%20not%20Test%20cricket%2C%26quot%3B%20Waugh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20neither%20Pakistan%20nor%20the%20West%20Indies%20sending%20their%20full-strength%20teams%20to%20Australia%20for%20the%20Test%20series%2C%20Waugh%20fears%20the%20trend%20will%20continue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20pretty%20obvious%20what%20the%20problem%20is.%20The%20West%20Indies%20aren't%20sending%20their%20full-strength%20side%20(to%20Australia%20this%20summer).%20They%20haven't%20picked%20a%20full-strength%20Test%20team%20for%20a%20couple%20of%20years%20now.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BSomeone%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%