mics%20and%20activists%2C%207.6%20crore%20workers%20have%20been%20deleted%20from%20the%20system%20over%20the%20last%2021%20months.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20data%20%E2%80%93%20according%20to%20the%20Union%20Rural%20Development%20Ministry%20%E2%80%93%20has%20it%20that%2034.8%20%25%20of%20job%20card%20holders%20remained%20ineligible%20for%20this%20mode%20of%20payment%20till%20as%20late%20as%20December%2027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Hindu%E2%80%99s%20sources%20in%20the%20government%2C%20however%2C%20claimed%20that%20till%20December%2027%2C%2012.7%25%20of%20active%20workers%20were%20yet%20unconnected%20to%20the%20payment%20system.%20%E2%80%98Active%20workers%E2%80%99%20are%20recognised%20as%20those%20who%20have%20worked%20for%20at%20least%20a%20single%20day%20over%20the%20last%20three%20financial%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20MGNREGA%20guarantees%20100%20days%20of%20work%20to%20rural%20households.%20Economist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Faadhaar-payments-compulsory-nrega%5C%22%3EJean%20Dreze%20had%20written%20for%20%3Cem%3EThe%3C%2Fem%3E%20%3Cem%3EWire%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20as%20far%2C%20%E2%80%9Cas%20recklessness%20goes%2C%20this%20is%20on%20par%20with%20a%20national%20lockdown%20at%20four%20hours%E2%80%99%20notice.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Narendra%20Modi%20government%20has%20attempted%20to%20weaken%20the%20essential%20job%20scheme%20despite%20its%20popularity%2C%20reducing%20allocation%20drastically%20in%20the%202023%20Budget%20%E2%80%93%20to%20Rs%2060%2C000%20crore%2C%20after%20the%20revised%20estimate%20for%20FY%E2%80%9923%20was%20at%20Rs%2089%2C400%20crore.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704097811000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2022%2F04%2F01113219%2FFLGCmSSaMAAeYIZ.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fmgnregs-aadhaar-system-payment%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Hindu's%20report%20notes%20that%20the%20govern