%2F1703871237-9778.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Findian-real-estate-in-2023-saw-highest-investment-inflows-since-2020-colliers-124010100274_1.html%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20leading%20sources%20of%20foreign%20capital%20in%20Indian%20real%20estate%20were%20Canada%20and%20Singapore%20accounting%20for%2078%25%20of%20the%20total%20inflows%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Findian-real-estate-in-2023-saw-highest-investment-inflows-since-2020-colliers-124010100274_1.html%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-business--standard-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Findian-real-estate-in-2023-saw-highest-investment-inflows-since-2020-colliers-124010100274_1.html%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.business-standard.com%2Famp%2Findustry%2Fnews%2Findian-real-estate-in-2023-saw-highest-investment-inflows-since-2020-colliers-124010100274_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22%26quot%3BBe%20Ready%20For%20Jail...%26quot%3B%3A%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20To%20Supporters%20Before%20Questioning%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EDelhi%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AAP%20convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Sunday%20said%20his%20party%20has%20gained%20popularity%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Bwork-centric%20politics%26quot%3B%20and%20asserted%20the%20party%20workers%20should%20be%20ready%20%26quot%3Bto%20go%20to%20jail%20for%20the%20paths%20we%20have%20chosen%20for%20the%20public%20good%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EChairing%20the%20National%20Executive%20and%2012th%20National%20Council%20meetings%20of%20the%20party%2C%20held%20virtually%20on%20Sunday%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BThe%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Party%20has%20risen%20to%20the%20third%20place%20among%201%2C350%20political%20parties%20in%20these%2010%20years.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIf%20we%20were%20not%20successful%20and%20did%20not%20do%20anything%20good%2C%20then%20none%20of%20our%20party%20leaders%20would%20have%20gone%20to%20jail%20and%20today%20everyone%20would%20have%20been%20happy%20with%20their%20families%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Kejriwal's%20remarks%20assume%20significance%20since%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20has%20asked%20him%20to%20appear%20before%20it%20on%20January%203%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20Delhi%20excise%20policy-linked%20money%20laundering%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Delhi%20CM%20said%20that%20two%20major%20parties%20have%20ruled%20this%20country%20for%2075%20years%20and%20said%20%26quot%3Bthese%20people%20will%20not%20relinquish%20power%20so%20easily%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20think%20we%20are%20facing%20a%20struggle%2C%20but%20there's%20no%20need%20for%20us%20to%20be%20saddened.%20Our%20five%20leaders%20who%20are%20in%20jail%20today%20are%20our%20heroes.%20We%20are%20very%20proud%20of%20all%20of%20them.%20I%20am%20continuously%20in%20touch%20with%20lawyers.%20It's%20a%20very%20good%20thing%20that%20even%20while%20in%20jail%2C%20all%20our%20leaders'%20spirits%20are%20still%20very%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOn%20the%20day%20Manish%20Sisodia's%20bail%20was%20cancelled%2C%20he%20sent%20a%20message%20saying%2C%20'It's%20okay%2C%20I'll%20stay%20in%20jail%20for%20as%20many%20days%20as%20needed.%20This%20entire%20case%20is%20fabricated%2C%20and%20my%20struggle%20will%20continue'%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20National%20Council%20meeting%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20asserted%20that%20the%20AAP%20has%20given%20the%20country%20a%20viable%20alternative%20in%20electoral%20politics%20and%20has%20gained%20popularity%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Bwork-centric%20politics%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20party%20workers%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you%20give%20good%20education%20to%20children%2C%20you%20will%20have%20to%20go%20to%20jail.%20If%20you%20provide%20free%20treatment%20to%20the%20poor%2C%20you%20will%20have%20to%20go%20to%20jail.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20go%20to%20jail%20for%20the%20paths%20we%20have%20chosen%20for%20public%20good.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20praised%20Punjab%20Chief%20Minister%20Bhagwant%20Mann%20for%20the%20remarkable%20progress%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20have%20shown%20what%20work%20can%20be%20done%20that%20other%20parties%20couldn't%20accomplish%20in%2075%20years.%20In%20the%20last%20two%20years%2C%20the%20work%20done%20by%20the%20AAP%20government%20in%20Punjab%20shows%20that%20if%20our%20government%20is%20in%20full%20power%20in%20a%20state%2C%20we%20can%20work%20very%20swiftly%20and%20do%20wonders%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20further%20said%20that%20AAP%20has%20made%20a%20significant%20impact%20on%20national%20politics%20in%2010%20years.%20For%20the%20first%20time%20in%20the%20country%2C%20opposition%20parties%20have%20been%20compelled%20to%20discuss%20schools%20and%20hospitals%2C%20he%20opined.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%2C%20these%20people%20have%20replaced%20manifesto%20with%20'guarantee'%20term%20stolen%20from%20us.%20They%20have%20started%20talking%20about%20'Modi's%20guarantee'%20and%20'Congress's%20guarantee'.%20These%20people%20have%20given%20guarantees%20to%20the%20public%2C%20but%20none%20of%20them%20fulfilled%20them%20because%20their%20intentions%20are%20not%20right%2C%20whereas%20we%20are%20fulfilling%20all%20our%20guarantees%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20informed%20the%20AAP%20officials%20about%20the%20national%20council%20and%20executive%20meetings%20of%20the%20party%20in%20physical%20mode%20in%20Amritsar%20in%20view%20of%20the%202024%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EExplaining%20the%20hurdles%20faced%20by%20the%20Delhi%20government%20and%20the%20freedom%20enjoyed%20in%20full-fledged%20state%20Punjab%2C%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20said%2C%20%26quot%3BIn%20Delhi%2C%20due%20to%20obstructions%20created%20by%20the%20LG%20and%20the%20Centre%2C%20we%20set%20up%20550%20Mohalla%20Clinics%20but%20in%20Punjab%20662%20Aam%20Aadmi%20Clinics%20(Mohalla%20Clinics)%20are%20operational%20now%20and%20by%20January%2026%2C%202024%2C%20the%20number%20will%20reach%20750%20in%20just%20two%20years.%26quot%3B%20He%20also%20asked%20the%20party%20workers%20to%20build%20and%20strengthen%20the%20organization%20across%20the%20country.%20Elections%20cannot%20be%20won%20without%20a%20strong%20organization%20in%20states%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20AAP%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections.%20We%20must%20contest%20well%20on%20the%20seats%20we%20get%20in%20seat%20sharing%2C%20and%20our%20entire%20effort%20will%20be%20to%20win%20all%20those%20seats.%20Volunteers%20of%20the%20party%20from%20states%20where%20the%20AAP%20isn't%20contesting%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%20will%20come%20and%20help%20in%20the%20places%20where%20elections%20are%20being%20contested%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%20the%20Haryana%20Assembly%20election%20is%20the%20most%20significant%20for%20the%20party%2C%20he%20said.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704093300000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2023-11%2Fth3aea4g_arvind-kejriwal_625x300_25_November_23.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhave-to-go-to-jail-for-paths-we-have-chosen-arvind-kejriwal-to-aap-workers-4777294%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Delhi%20Chief%20Minister%20and%20AAP%20convener%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20Sunday%20said%20his%20party%20has%20gained%20popularity%20for%20its%20%26quot%3Bwork-centric%20politics%26quot%3B%20and%20asserted%20the%20party%20workers%20should%20be%20ready%20%26quot%3Bto%20go%20to%20jail%20for%20th