id%20%26quot%3Bpredictions%20of%20the%20fall%20of%20Bihar%20government%20and%20JDU%20split%20are%20far%20from%20truth%26quot%3B.%20%26quot%3BThe%20Nitish%20Kumar-led%20alliance%20government%20is%20going%20strong%20in%20Bihar.%20In%20the%20upcoming%20Lok%20Sabha%20polls%2C%20we%20will%20fight%20together%20from%20the%20INDIA%20platform.%20Bihar%20will%20show%20the%20way%20for%20the%20farewell%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20(Prime%20Minister%20Narendra)%20Modi.%20The%20people%20have%20made%20up%20their%20minds%2C%26quot%3B%20Mr%20Singh%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAfter%20Mr%20Singh%20stepped%20down%20as%20JDU%20chief%2C%20Bihar%20Chief%20Minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20took%20over%20the%20post%20during%20the%20JDU's%20national%20executive%20meeting%20at%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20Mr%20Singh%20has%20said%20he%20quit%20the%20top%20post%20owing%20to%20engagements%20in%20his%20Lok%20Sabha%20constituency%2C%20the%20BJP%20has%20claimed%20he%20was%20removed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBJP%20leader%20from%20Bihar%2C%20Shahnawaz%20Hussain%2C%20told%20news%20agency%20ANI%2C%20%26quot%3BNitish%20Kumar%20ji%20first%20made%20RCP%20Singh%20president%2C%20then%20Lalan%20Singh%20and%20now%20he%20himself%20has%20become%20president%20of%20JD%20(U).%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Singh%20has%20said%20he%20would%20sue%20media%20outfits%20publishing%20reports%20that%20he%20had%20plotted%20a%20rebellion%20against%20Nitish%20Kumar%20in%20favour%20of%20Rashtriya%20Janata%20leader%20Tejashwi%20Yadav.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20statement%2C%20he%20said%20the%20reports%20in%20%26quot%3Bone%20major%20newspaper%20and%20some%20news%20channels%26quot%3B%20were%20%26quot%3Bcompletely%20misleading%2C%20false%20and%20aimed%20at%20tarnishing%20my%20reputation%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704093120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-01%2Fg8s5jnho_lalan-singh-pti_625x300_01_January_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frajiv-ranjan