%3Cp%3EAhead%20of%20his%20final%20Test%20match%20at%20his%20home%20arena%20of%20Sydney%20Cricket%20Ground%20(SCG)%2C%20Australian%20opener%20David%20Warner%20reflected%20on%20the%202018%20ball-tampering%20scandal%20in%20Cape%20Town%20that%20led%20to%20a%20one-year%20ban%20from%20cricket%20and%20a%20ban%20from%20assuming%20leadership%20roles%20in%20Australia%2C%20saying%20that%20the%20issue%20could%20have%20been%20handled%20differently%20but%20he%20has%20moved%20on%20from%20it.%20Warner%20will%20bid%20farewell%20to%20the%20longest%20format%20of%20the%20game%20with%20the%20third%20Test%20against%20Pakistan%20at%20his%20home%20arena%20of%20Sydney%20Cricket%20Ground%20(SCG).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20being%20asked%20if%20he%20holds%20any%20bitterness%20over%20his%20suspension%20and%20leadership%20ban%20handled%20by%20Cricket%20Australia%2C%20Warner%20said%20that%20he%20has%20moved%20on%20from%20the%20issue%20though%20it%20could%20have%20been%20handled%20differently.%20Since%20then%2C%20he%20has%20enjoyed%20his%20leadership%20roles%20in%20T20%20leagues%20worldwide%2C%20but%20for%20him%2C%20leadership%20is%20no%20about%20a%20badge%2C%20but%20setting%20an%20example%20both%20on%20the%20field%20and%20away%20from%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20knew%20a%20question%20like%20this%20was%20going%20to%20come%20up.%20When%20I%20look%20back%20at%20that%2C%20it%20can%20be%20handled%20differently.%20But%20I%20think%20Nick%20(Hockley%2C%20CA's%20chief%20executive)%20did%20his%20ultimate%20best%20to%20put%20that%20forward%20to%20the%20board%20and%20the%20decision%20was%20made%2C%20and%20I%20am%20happy%20with%20that.%20I%20have%20moved%20forward%20from%20that.%20I%20have%20got%20opportunities%20to%20lead%20in%20the%20IPL%2C%20to%20lead%20in%20the%20ILT20.%20I%20have%20enjoyed%20my%20leadership%20roles%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Warner%20as%20quoted%20by%20ESPNCricinfo.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20for%20me%2C%20in%20recent%20years%2C%20I%20have%20learned%20that%20leadership%20(is%20not%20about)%20wearing%20a%20captain%20or%20vice-captain%20badges.%20It%20is%20about%20being%20true%20to%20yourself%2C%20and%20setting%20an%20example%20both%20on%20and%20off%20the%20field.%20For%20me%2C%20I%20think%20I'm%20a%20leader%20in%20this%20team%20no%20matter%20what.%20You%20do%20not%20need%20that%20C%20or%20VC%20next%20to%20your%20name.%20I%20know%20myself%20and%20my%20energy%20at%20times%20can%20be%20annoying%2C%20and%20I%20can%20be%20a%20pest%2C%20but%20I%20know%20that%20inside%20that%20changeroom%20it%20gets%20everyone%20up%20and%20about%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%202018%20Ball-Tampering%20Scandal%2C%20also%20known%20as%20the%20'Sandpaper%20Gate'%2C%20then-Australian%20captain%20Steve%20Smith%2C%20vice-captain%20David%20Warner%20and%20batter%20Cameron%20Bancroft%20received%20heavy%20sanctions%20from%20Cricket%20Australia%20for%20their%20involvement%20in%20ball-tampering%20during%20the%20series%20against%20South%20Africa.%20It%20all%20started%20when%20Bancroft%20was%20caught%20by%20cameras%20trying%20to%20tamper%20with%20the%20condition%20of%20the%20ball%20using%20sandpaper%20hidden%20in%20his%20cricket%20gear.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20learnings%20from%20the%20ball-tampering%20scandal%2C%20Warner%20said%20when%20he%20left%20South%20Africa%2C%20he%20attended%20a%20big%20church%20convention%20and%20started%20playing%20grade%20cricket%20to%20make%20his%20way%20back%20into%20the%20team.%20He%20also%20got%20to%20spend%20time%20with%20his%20children%2C%20which%20he%20loved%20and%20wanted%20to%20make%20every%20child%20who%20dreamt%20of%20ever%20playing%20have%20an%20ambition%20of%20playing%20for%20Australia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhen%20I%20left%20South%20Africa%2C%20the%20first%20five%20or%20six%20people%20that%20came%20up%20to%20me%20were%20priests%20and%20gave%20me%20a%20card.%20Then%20we%20went%20on%20a%20holiday%20to%20Singapore%20after%20that%20and%20there%20was%20a%20big%20church%20convention.%20I%20then%20sat%20back%20and%20spoke%20to%20Candice%2C%20and%20said%20someone%20was%20clearly%20watching%20down%20upon%20us.%20I%20just%20grew%20strength%20from%20there%20to%20go%20back%2C%20play%20grade%20cricket%2C%20get%20a%20sense%20of%20that%20cricket%20community%20back%20-%20the%20canteen%20ladies%2C%20people%20who%20run%20the%20drinks%20out%2C%20taking%20on%20and%20off%20the%20covers%20-%20it%20was%20a%20sense%20of%20something%20I%20sort%20of%20got%20disconnected%20with.%20I%20think%20a%20lot%20of%20us%20do%20because%20we%20are%20in%20that%20bubble%20but%20when%20you%20go%20back%20and%20see%20the%20real%20people%20who%20are%20working%20hard%2C%20which%20we%20did%20as%20young%20kids%2C%20that%20is%20what%20I%20reflect%20most%20upon%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Warner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20I%20can%20keep%20continuing%20to%20make%20sure%20that%20people%20understand%20where%20you%20come%20from%20and%20how%20you%20got%20to%20where%20you%20are%2C%20that%20is%20going%20to%20be%20very%20important.%20That%20is%20a%20lesson%20that%20I%20learned.%20Then%20spending%20time%20at%20home%20with%20the%20kids%2C%20was%20unbelievable.%20I%20actually%20really%20enjoyed%20that.%20I%20spent%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20with%20my%20wife.%20We%20are%20sort%20of%20disconnected%20in%20a%20way%20when%20we%20travel%20a%20lot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BReflecting%20back%20on%20that%20whole%20period%2C%20my%20whole%20career%2C%20I%20have%20got%20no%20regrets%20because%20you%20are%20going%20to%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20hurdles%20you%20are%20going%20to%20have%20to%20jump.%20There%20are%20going%20to%20be%20obstacles%20in%20the%20way%2C%20but%20you%20have%20to%20move%20forward%20and%20I%20have%20done%20that%20with%20dignity.%20I%20have%20got%20a%20lot%20of%20passion%20for%20the%20game%20and%20it%20was%20important%20from%20my%20perspective%20that%20I%20am%20giving%20back%2C%20making%20sure%20that%20I%20gained%20the%20respect%20back%20but%20making%20sure%20I%20am%20putting%20Australian%20cricket%20fir