%20of%20Michael%20Schumacher%20is%20huge.%20Since%20his%20skiing%20accident%20in%202013%2C%20the%20F1%20great%20has%20not%20appeared%20in%20public.%20December%2029%2C%202023%2C%20was%20the%2010th%20anniversary%20of%20the%20F1%20great's%20accident%20in%20the%20French%20Alps.%20German%20publication%20BILD%20has%20come%20up%20with%20a%20new%20report%20where%20it%20claims%20to%20have%20fresh%20details%20about%20Michael%20Schumacher's%20daily%20routine%20on%20the%2010th%20anniversary%20of%20that%20accident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMultiple%20publications%20like%20Daily%20Mail%2C%20PlanetF1%2C%20quoted%20the%20report%20which%20provides%20fresh%20updates%20on%20Michael%20Schumacher.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20the%20report%2C%20Michael%20Schumacher%20has%20been%20driven%20in%20a%20Mercedes%20AMG%20car%20to%20stimulate%20the%20brain%20with%20familiar%20sounds.%20This%20was%20done%2C%20according%20to%20the%20report%2C%20because%20the%20racing%20great%20spent%20over%20two%20decades%20in%20Formula%20One%20or%20in%20other%20classes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20report%20adds%20that%20Michael%20Schumacher%20receives%2024-hour%20care%2C%20with%20a%20private%20infirmary%20situated%20in%20his%20former%20office.%2015%20doctors%20and%20their%20assistants%20ensure%20his%20well-being.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENow%20in%20a%20new%20interview%2C%20Michael%20Schumacher's%20former%20Ferrari%20teammate%20Rubens%20Barrichello%20said%20what%20happened%20when%20he%20asked%20the%20F1%20great's%20family%20the%20permission%20to%20meet%20him%20after%20his%20accident.%20%C2%A0%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWith%20Schumacher%2C%20I%20called%20once%20and%20said%20I%20wanted%20to%20visit%20him%2C%26quot%3B%20Rubens%20Barrichello%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20By%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thesun.co.uk%2Fsport%2F25202941%2Frubens-barrichello-ferrari-banned-michael-schumacher-accident-f1%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Sun%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20Flow%20Podcast.%20%26quot%3BThey%20told%20me%20that%20unfortunately%20I%20wouldn't%20be%20helping%20and%20that%20I%20might%20be%20sad.%20So%20I%20understood%20that%20at%20that%20moment%20it%20was%20not%20the%20time%20to%20enter%20%5Bhis%20life%5D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBarrichello%20and%20Schumacher%20were%20teammates%20at%20Ferrari%20from%202000%20to%202005.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMichael%20Schumacher%20was%20very%20close%20to%20former%20F1%20champion%20Sebastian%20Vettel%2C%20who%20is%20also%20from%20the%20same%20country%20and%20has%20driven%20for%20teams%20like%20Ferrari%2C%20Red%20Bull.%20Vettel%20recently%20opened%20up%20on%20their%20relationship%20in%20an%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt's%20still%20very%2C%20very%20difficult%20to%2C%20I%20don't%20want%20to%20say%20accept%2C%20but%20to%20accept%20that%20he%20keeps%20fighting%20and%20he's%20not%20doing%20well.%20Of%20course%20I%20wish%20him%20only%20the%20best.%20It%20is%20still%20a%20topic%20very%20often%20and%20I%20think%20about%20it%20sometimes%20in%20silence%20and%20sometimes%20a%20lot%2C%26quot%3B%20was%20quoted%20as%20saying%20by%20RTL%20in%20the%20English%20version%20of%20its%20interview.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EVettel%20also%20revealed%20how%20he%20reacted%20to%20the%20heartbreaking%20news%20of%20Schumacher's%20skiing%20accident%20at%20the%20end%20of%20December%202013.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20first%20thoughts%20were%20of%20course%20at%20the%20last%20conversation%20we%20had%20together%2C%26quot%3B%20remembers%20Vettel.%20%26quot%3BI%20told%20him%20that%20I%20was%20going%20to%20be%20a%20father%20and%20what%20was%20coming%20for%20us.%20I%20just%20miss%20my%20friend.%20He%20would%20have%20been%20so%20important%20in%20recent%20years.%20I%20would%20have%20had%20so%20many%20questions%20and%20he%20certainly%20could%20have%20provided%20so%20many%20answers%20or%20inspiration.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704092040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2021-08%2Fanqa