20allegedly%20moving%20one%20more%20project%20from%20the%20state%20to%20Gujarat.%20According%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.deccanchronicle.com%2Fnation%2Fpolitics%2F311223%2Fopposition-targets-shinde-over-alleged-shifting-of-project-to-gujarat.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20India%E2%80%99s%20first%20submarine%20project%2C%20planned%20at%20Nivati%20Rock%20in%20Maharashtra%E2%80%99s%20Sindhudurg%20district%2C%20is%20now%20expected%20to%20come%20up%20at%20Dwarka%20in%20Gujarat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20project%20was%20announced%20by%20the%20Maharashtra%20government%20in%202018%2C%20and%20Rs%2056%20crore%20was%20to%20be%20set%20aside%20for%20it.%20However%2C%20the%20project%20did%20not%20get%20off%20the%20ground.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EDeccan%20Herald%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3Ereports%20that%20the%20Gujarat%20government%20has%20stated%20that%20this%20project%20will%20now%20be%20built%20in%20Dwarka%2C%20and%20signed%20an%20agreement%20with%20the%20Mazagon%20Dock%20Limited%20(MDL).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShiv%20Sena%20(UBT)%20MLA%20Vaibhav%20Naik%20lashed%20out%20at%20the%20Shinde%20government%20over%20this%20on%20Sunday%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fmumbai-news%2Frumours-of-another-project-going-to-gujarat-lead-to-uproar-101704044477340.html%5C%22%3Esaying%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20project%20was%20declared%20a%20few%20years%20ago.%20During%20the%20MVA%20government%E2%80%99s%20tenure%2C%20a%20budgetary%20allocation%20was%20made%20for%20it.%20Marine%20expert%20Sarang%20Kulkarni%20was%20appointed%20as%20a%20consultant%2C%20and%20there%20were%20primary%20discussions%20about%20purchasing%20the%20submarine%20for%20around%20Rs%20200%20crore.%20But%20ever%20since%20the%20Shinde-Fadnavis%20government%20took%20over%2C%20there%20has%20been%20no%20development%20on%20this%20front.%20Now%20we%20have%20discovered%20that%20the%20project%20is%20being%20shifted%20to%20Dwarka%20in%20Gujarat.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENationalist%20Congress%20Party%20leader%20Sanjay%20Raut%20also%20criticised%20this%20change%2C%20adding%20that%20the%20Shinde-Fadnavis%20government%20seemed%20to%20be%20moving%20a%20large%20number%20of%20projects%20to%20Gujarat.%20%C2%A0%E2%80%9CGujarat%20has%20taken%20away%2017%20projects%20of%20Maharashtra%20but%20CM%20Eknath%20Shinde%20and%20DCM%20Devendra%20Fadnavis%20are%20not%20uttering%20a%20word%20against%20it.%20This%20is%20nothing%20but%20robbery.%20Gujarat%20is%20taking%20away%20projects%20that%20give%20employment%20to%20the%20youth%20and%20in%20return%20supplying%20drugs%20which%20destroy%20the%20youth%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcities%2Fmumbai-news%2Frumours-of-another-project-going-to-gujarat-lead-to-uproar-101704044477340.html%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHow%20many%20more%20projects%20is%20this%20state%20government%20going%20to%20gift%20to%20Gujarat%3F%E2%80%9D%20said%20Congress%20leader%20Vijay%20Wadettiwar.%20%E2%80%9COne%20after%20another%2C%20projects%20have%20been%20taken%20there%20but%20the%20CM%20and%20two%20DCMs%20only%20go%20to%20Delhi%20to%20salute%20their%20political%20masters.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShinde%2C%20on%20the%20other%20hand%2C%20has%20claimed%20that%20allegations%20that%20the%20project%20has%20been%20shifted%20to%20Gujarat%20are%20false.%20%E2%80%9CNo%20projects%20are%20going%20to%20Gujarat.%20Don%E2%80%99t%20believe%20in%20false%20news%20being%20particularly%20spread%20by%20the%20opposition.%20The%20tourism%20minister%20is%20with%20me%2C%20he%20also%20confirmed%20saying%20no%20such%20project%20has%20left%20the%20states.%20What%20about%20projects%20which%20were%20stalled%20by%20the%20MVA.%20We%20have%20not%20just%20re-started%20them%20but%20are%20also%20completing%20them%20at%20full%20speed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said%2C%20according%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fmumbai%2Fmva-shinde-fadnavis-government-now-spar-over-submarine-project-going-to-gujarat%2Farticleshow%2F106422859.cms%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704084954000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F13120212%2Fdownload.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmaharashtra-opposition-hits-out-at-shinde-govt-after-submarine-project-moved-to-gujarat%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22India's%20first%20submarine%20project%2C%20planned%20at%20Nivati%20Rock%20in%20Maharashtra's%20Sindhudurg%20district%2C%20is%20now%20expected%20to%20come%20up%20at%20Dwarka%20in%20Gujarat.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A11%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fmaharashtra-opposition-hits-out-at-shinde-govt-after-submarine-project-moved-to-gujarat%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%226%20killed%2C%20two%20critical%20after%20car%20rams%20divider%20in%20Jharkhand's%20Jamshedpur%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704084463000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-106434208%2Cimgsize-76883.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fjamshedpur%2Fsix-killed-two-critical-after-car-rams-divider-in-jharkhands-jamshedpur%2Farticleshow%2F106433722.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20CITY%20DESK%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fjamshedpur%2Fsix-killed-two-critical-after-car-rams-divider-in-jharkhands-jamshedpur%2Farticleshow%2F106433722.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22US%20woman%20accused%20of%20killing%20two%20of%20her%20children%20arrested%20in%20UK%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1704084120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3